%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20Singapore%20Airlines%20airlifted%20a%20giant%20panda%20cub%20and%20sent%20it%20on%20its%20journey%20home%20to%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Giant%20panda%20cub%2C%20Le%20Le%20(left)%20and%20his%20crate%20being%20locked%20into%20position%20on%20SIA's%20Boeing%20747-400F%20freighter%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a88d0f43bb77284b9dfced%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGiant%20panda%20cub%2C%20Le%20Le%20(left)%20traveled%20from%20Singapore%20to%20China%20via%20Singapore%20Airlines%20on%2016%20January%202024.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3B%20Singapore%20Airlines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESingapore's%20first%20giant%20panda%20cub%2C%20Le%20Le%2C%20traveled%20to%20China%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20panda%20cub%20took%20a%204.5-hour-long%20flight%20to%20China%20via%20Singapore%20Airlines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20flag%20carrier%20said%20it%20spent%20the%20past%20five%20months%20preparing%20for%20Le%20Le's%20trip%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Airlines%20was%20given%20a%20monumental%20task%20in%20January%3A%20They%20were%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20sending%20Le%20Le%2C%20a%202.5-year-old%20giant%20panda%20cub%2C%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20August%202021%2C%20Le%20Le%20was%20Singapore's%20first%20giant%20panda%20cub.%20The%20cub's%20parents%2C%20Kai%20Kai%20and%20Jia%20Jia%2C%20traveled%20to%20Singapore%20on%20loan%20in%202012.%20Both%20pandas%20are%20set%20to%20return%20to%20China%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Le%2C%20however%2C%20has%20to%20be%20separated%20from%20his%20parents.%20Due%20to%20conservation%20concerns%2C%20China%20requires%20host%20countries%20to%20return%20any%20cubs%20born%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20back%20home%20was%20a%20complicated%20one%20to%20execute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Singapore%20Airlines%20team%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20five%20months%20poring%20through%20every%20little%20detail%20to%20prepare%20for%20this%20special%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gajandran%20Sokayan%2C%20an%20assistant%20manager%20at%20the%20airline%20who%20oversees%20dangerous%20goods%20and%20special%20cargo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPre-flight%20preparation%20began%20back%20in%20December%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Giant%20panda%20cub%20Le%20Le.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a895686979d73718243302%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELe%20Le's%20panda%20care%20team%20had%20to%20use%20positive%20reinforcement%20training%20to%20get%20him%20accustomed%20to%20his%20custom%20travel%20crate.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Le%20made%20one%20last%20public%20appearance%20in%20Singapore%20on%20December%2013%20at%20River%20Wonders%2C%20Singapore's%20river-themed%20wildlife%20park.%20The%20cub%20went%20into%20quarantine%20for%20the%20big%20journey%20on%20December%2014.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20zoo's%20team%20then%20used%20positive%20reinforcement%20training%20to%20familiarize%20the%20cub%20with%20a%20custom%20travel%20crate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crate%20was%20equipped%20with%20removable%20plywood%20boards%20for%20feedings%20and%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20to%20the%20airport%20while%20beating%20the%20Singaporean%20heat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Le%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20transported%20from%20the%20zoo%20to%20the%20airport%20using%20a%20reefer%20truck.%20The%20truck%20had%20to%20be%20kept%20at%20a%20temperature%20of%20between%2012%C2%B0C%20and%2016%C2%B0C.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a896f8dcdb354a98587958%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELe%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20transported%20from%20the%20zoo%20to%20the%20airport%20using%20a%20reefer%20truck.%20The%20truck%20had%20to%20be%20kept%20at%20a%20temperature%20of%20between%2012%C2%B0C%20and%2016%C2%B0C.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20big%20move%2C%20Le%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20transported%20from%20the%20zoo%20to%20the%20airport%20with%20an%20air-conditioned%20truck.%20The%20truck's%20temperature%20was%20kept%20between%2012%20and%2016%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20keep%20things%20nice%20and%20cool%20for%20the%20furry%20traveler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERiding%20safely%20on%20a%20pallet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Le%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20secured%20to%20a%20pallet%20before%20it%20was%20loaded%20onto%20the%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a89a9adcdb354a985879a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELe%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20secured%20to%20a%20pallet%20before%20it%20was%20loaded%20onto%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20Le%20Le's%20crate%20had%20to%20be%20secured%20to%20a%20pallet%20before%20loading%20it%20onto%20the%20plane.%20This%20pallet%20also%20contained%20travel%20essentials%20for%20the%20giant%20panda%20cub.%20The%20total%20weight%20of%20the%20palletized%20crate%20was%20around%20600%20kilograms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENo%20boarding%20queues%20for%20this%20young%20traveler%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226017%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Le%20Le's%20crate%20was%20loaded%20through%20the%20nose%20of%20SIA's%20Boeing%20747-400F%20freighter%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a89ce06979d7371824336d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224013%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELe%20Le's%20crate%20was%20loaded%20through%20the%20nose%20of%20SIA's%20Boeing%20747-400F%20freighter%20aircraft.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pallet%20was%20then%20loaded%20through%20the%20nose%20of%20SIA's%20Boeing%20747-400F%20freighter%20aircraft.%20Like%20the%20reefer%20truck%2C%20the%20plane%20had%20to%20be%20pre-cooled%20one%20hour%20before%20boarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cargo%20personnel%20moving%20Le%20Le's%20crate%20into%20position%20on%20the%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a89e0643bb77284b9dfe3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECargo%20personnel%20moving%20Le%20Le's%20crate%20into%20position%20on%20the%20aircraft.%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Airlines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pallet%20was%20then%20locked%20in%20position%20on%20the%20aircraft%20before%20takeoff%20to%20reduce%20movement%20during%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFarewell%20little%20one%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20nose%20of%20the%20aircraft%20closes%20as%20it%20gets%20ready%20for%20take-off.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a89ed443bb77284b9dfe46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20nose%20of%20the%20aircraft%20closes%20as%20it%20gets%20ready%20for%20take-off.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Le%20didn't%20travel%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20accompanied%20by%20a%20keeper%20and%20veterinarian%20from%20Singapore%20and%20a%20zookeeper%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20giant%20panda%20cub%20was%20also%20served%20a%20special%20in-flight%20meal%20during%20his%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20bamboo%2C%20bamboo%20shoots%2C%20fruit%2C%20pellets%2C%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESIA%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Wednes