violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state%20last%20year%20over%20the%20Meitie%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%20The%20demand%20was%20opposed%20by%20the%20tribal%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%2C%20weapons%20were%20looted%20from%20security%20installations%2C%20arming%20militants%20and%20fuelling%20a%20cycle%20of%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20attack%20in%20Moreh%20yesterday%2C%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20secretariat.%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20and%20MLAs%20were%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705548900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhq6tt5ro_manipur-violence_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-border-force-personnel-injured-in-fresh-mob-violence-in-manipur-4883989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20incident%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20three%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20personnel%20were%20injured%20last%20night%20when%20a%20mob%20attacked%20police%20headquarters%20in%20Thoubal%20district%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-border-force-personnel-injured-in-fresh-mob-violence-in-manipur-4883989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandigarh%20mayoral%20polls%3A%20It's%20INDIA%20vs%20BJP%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705548873000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106944078%2Cimgsize-36542.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fchandigarh-mayoral-polls-today-its-india-vs-bjp-why-congress-aap-pact-is-no-guarantee-for-punjab-tie-up%2Farticleshow%2F106943956.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Today's%20polls%20in