%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoor-opens-up-about-challenges-shooting-intimate-scenes-in-animal-credits-alia-bhatts-support%2Farticleshow%2F106942862.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2236%20Runs%20In%20An%20Over%2C%202%20Tie%20Breaks%3A%20Why%20Ind%20vs%20Afg%20T20I%20Was%20A%20Historic%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20mayhem%20ruled%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20stadium%20in%20Bengaluru%20as%20India%20edged%20Afghanistan%20in%20a%20humdinger%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20duo%20broke%20a%20plethora%20of%20records%20en%20route%20to%20their%20unbeaten%20190-run%20stand%20in%20the%203rd%20and%20final%20T20I%20of%20the%20series.%20India%20weren't%20in%20the%20best%20of%20position%20when%20Rinku%20came%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20having%20lost%204%20batters%20at%20the%20score%20of%2022%20runs%20but%20the%20duo%20remained%20unbeaten%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20innings%2C%20guiding%20the%20team%20to%20a%20total%20of%20212%20runs%2C%20capping%20off%20the%20innings%20by%20scoring%2036%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20slammed%20121%20runs%20off%2069%20balls%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20eight%20sixes%20while%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Rinku%20played%20an%20unbeaten%20knock%20of%2069%20runs%20from%2039%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes%20in%20his%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cstrong%3EFull%20List%20of%20Records%20India%20shattered%20in%20double%20Super%20Over%20win%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%203rd%20T20I%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighest%20T20I%20partnership%20for%20any%20wicket%20for%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20and%20Rinku%20stitched%20together%20an%20unbeaten%20partnership%20of%20190%20runs%20against%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E190*%20R%20Sharma%20-%20R%20Singh%20v%20Afg%20Bengaluru%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E176%20S%20Samson%20-%20D%20Hooda%20v%20Ire%20Dublin%202022%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E165%20R%20Sharma%20-%20KL%20Rahul%20v%20SL%20Indore%202017%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E165%20Y%20Jaiswal%20-%20S%20Gill%20v%20WI%20Lauderhill%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighest%20individual%20scores%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20Sharma's%20highest%20score%20in%20a%20T20I%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20121*%20is%20the%20highest%20for%20the%20captain%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%20for%20India%2C%20but%20the%20fourth-highest%20individual%20score%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is.%20The%20list%20is%20led%20by%20Shubman%20Gill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E126*%20Shubman%20Gill%20v%20NZ%20Ahmedabad%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E123*%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20v%20Aus%20Guwahati%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E122*%20Virat%20Kohli%20v%20Afg%20Dubai%202022%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E121*%20Rohit%20Sharma%20v%20Afg%20Bengaluru%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E212%20-%20Highest%20total%20for%20a%20team%20after%20losing%204%20wickets%20for%2025%20runs%20or%20less%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20T20I%20saw%20India%20posting%20the%20highest%20total%20for%20a%20team%20after%20being%20four%20down%20for%2025%20or%20less%2C%20reaching%20212%2F4.%20The%20previous%20best%20was%20by%20the%20USA%20against%20Ireland%20in%20Lauderhill%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E212%2F4%20Ind%20vs%20Afg%20Bengaluru%202024%20(from%2022%2F4)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E188%2F6%20USA%20vs%20Ire%20Lauderhill%202021%20(from%2016%2F4)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E174%2F10%20Philippines%20vs%20Cambodia%20Phnom%20Penh%202023%20(from%2023%2F4)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20runs%20scored%20in%20an%20over%20in%20T20Is%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20of%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20helped%20India%20score%2036%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over%20of%20the%20match%2C%20courtesy%20of%20a%20no-ball.%20Only%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20and%20Kieron%20Pollard%20had%20earlier%20scored%2036%20runs%20each%2C%20for%20India%20against%20England%20(vs%20Stuart%20Broad%20in%20Durban%20in%202007)%20and%20for%20West%20Indies%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20(vs%20Akila%20Dananjaya%20in%20Coolidge%20in%202021)%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E36%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20off%20Stuart%20Broad%20Durban%202007%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E36%20Kieron%20Pollard%20off%20Akila%20Dananjaya%20Coolidge%202021%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E36%20Rohit%20Sharma%20%26amp%3B%20Rinku%20Singh%20off%20Karim%20Janat%20Bengaluru%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst-ever%20double%20Super%20Over%20in%20an%20international%20match%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20over%2015%20matches%20ending%20in%20a%20tie%20since%20the%20multiple%20Super%20Over%20rule%20came%20into%20existence%20after%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20controversy%2C%20there%20had%20never%20been%20a%20double%20Super%20Over%20until%20the%20India%20vs%20Afghanistan%20clash%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20other%20records%20that%20were%20broken%20in%20Bengaluru%20during%20India%20vs%20Afghanistan%203rd%20T20I%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Rinku%20Singh's%20unbeaten%20partnership%20of%20190%20runs%20is%20the%20highest%20for%20any%20side%20at%205th%20wicket%20or%20below%20in%20T20Is.%20The%20previous%20best%20was%20145%20runs%20between%20Deependra%20Airee%20%26amp%3B%20Kushal%20Malla%20for%20Nepal%20vs%20Hong%20Kong%20in%20Mulpani.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20this%20series%20win%2C%20India%20now%20have%209%20whitewash%20series%20wins%20in%20T20I%20cricket%20-%20the%20most%20by%20any%20country%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%20of%20the%20sport.%20Pakistan%20are%20next%2C%20with%208%20such%20clean%20sweeps.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERohit%20now%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20scoring%20the%20most%20runs%20as%20an%20Indian%20captain%20in%20T20Is.%20He%20went%20past%20Virat%20Kohli's%20tally%20of%201570%20runs%20in%2050%20T20Is%2C%20courtesy%20of%20his%20121-run%20knock.%20He%20now%20sits%20at%201648%20runs%20in%20T20Is.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERohit%20is%20now%20the%20second%20captain%20after%20Babar%20Azam%20to%20hit%20three%20T20I%20centuries%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20third%20T20I%20for%20India%20helped%20Rohit%20equal%20MS%20Dhoni's%20record%20of%20winning%2042%20T20Is%20for%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Hitman%20sits%20top%20of%20the%20list%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20number%20of%20bilateral%20T20I%20series%20wins%20for%20India%20as%20captain.%20Rohit%20has%2012%20to%20his%20name.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705548480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fb55qqn5g_rinku-singh-and-rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Frohit-sharma-rinku-singh-mayhem-breaks-plethora-of-records-in-3rd-t20i-full-list-4882418%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20broken%20several%20records%20in%20the%203rd%20T20I%20against%20Afghanistan%20after%20the%20match%20required%20two%20Super%20Overs%20to%20conclude%20the%20result.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20judge%20bench-slaps%20Trump's%20attorney%2014%20times%20over%20basic%20lawyering%20in%20a%20single%20day%20of%20testimony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20attends%20the%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20defamation%20trial%20in%20New%20York%20with%20attorney%20Alina%20Habba.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a8508