pika%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705546947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106942482%2Cimgsize-91152.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-orry-says-he-never-wants-to-relate-to-deepika-padukone-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F106942483.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106942483.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOrry%2C%20aka%20Orhan%20Awatramani%2C%20captivates%20social%20media%20with%20his%20unique%20humor%2C%20hand%20pose%2C%20and%20quirky%20antics.%20He%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Koffee%20with%20Karan%2C%20sharing%20insights%20into%20his%20fame%2C%20strategies%2C%20and%20favorite%20episodes.%20Orry%20prefers%20not%20to%20relate%20to%20Deepika%20Padukone%20but%20admires%20her.%20He%20also%20enjoys%20episodes%20with%20the%20Kapoor%20sisters%20and%20Rani%20Mukerji%20and%20Kajol.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-orry-says-he-never-wants-to-relate-to-deepika-padukone-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F106942483.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWanted%20Someone%20Like%20That%20At...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Drops%20Big%20Rinku%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Hint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20India's%20win%20over%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20third%20T20I%20following%20two%20Super%20Overs%2C%20Indian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20lauded%20middle-order%20batter%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20off%20age%26quot%3B%20and%20knows%20his%20strengths%20well.%20Rohit's%20record-breaking%20fifth%20T20I%20century%20and%20half-centuries%20by%20Afghanistan%20top%20order%20batters%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%2C%20skipper%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20and%20Gulbadin%20Naib%20could%20not%20separate%20both%20sides%20as%20Men%20in%20Blue%20beat%20a%20spirited%20Afghan%20side%20in%20the%20second%20over%20at%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20match%2C%20talking%20about%20batting%20during%20the%20match%20and%20both%20Super%20Overs%2C%20a%20total%20of%20three%20times%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20remember%20when%20was%20the%20last%20time%20this%20happened.%20I%20think%20I%20batted%203%20times%20in%20one%20of%20the%20IPL%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20his%20partnership%20of%20190%20runs%20with%20him%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCreating%20the%20partnership%20was%20important%20and%20we%20(Rinku%20and%20I)%20kept%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20to%20not%20lose%20that%20intent%20in%20big%20games%20and%20it%20was%20a%20good%20game%20for%20us%20to%20be%20in%2C%20the%20pressure%20was%20there%20and%20was%20important%20to%20bat%20long%20and%20deep%20and%20not%20compromise%20on%20the%20intent%20we%20want%20to%20show.%20The%20last%20couple%20of%20series%20that%20he%20played%2C%20he%20showed%20what%20he%20can%20do%20with%20the%20bat.%20Very%20calm%20and%20knows%20his%20strength%20pretty%20well.%20He%20is%20coming%20of%20age%20and%20doing%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20him%20and%20he%20has%20done%20well%20for%20India.%20It%20augurs%20well%20for%20the%20team%20moving%20forward%2C%20wanted%20someone%20like%20that%20at%20the%20backend%20and%20we%20know%20what%20he%20has%20done%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20he%20has%20carried%20that%20to%20the%20Indian%20colours%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%2015%20games%20and%2011%20innings%20in%20T20Is%20for%20India%2C%20Rinku%20has%20scored%20356%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2089.00%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20176%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%20He%20has%20been%20making%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20as%20a%20finisher%20for%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20was%20reduced%20to%2022%2F4.%20Following%20this%2C%20Rohit%20(121*%20in%2069%20balls%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20eight%20sixes)%20and%20Rinku%20(69*%20in%2039%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20took%20India%20to%20212%2F4%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFareed%20Ahmed%20(3%2F20)%20was%20the%20best%20bowler%20for%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20Gurbaz%20(50%20in%2032%20balls%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Zadran%20(50%20in%2041%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20a%20six)%20gave%20Afghanistan%20a%20fine%20start%20with%20a%2093-run%20opening%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20Naib%20(55*%20in%2023%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20four%20sixes)%20joined%20forces%20with%20Mohammed%20Nabi%20(34%20in%2016%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20to%20help%20Afghanistan%20tie%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20Sundar%20(3%2F18)%20was%20India's%20top%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Super%20Over%20ended%20in%20a%20tie%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20scoring%2016%20runs%20each.%20A%20notable%20moment%20in%20the%20game%20saw%20Rohit%20walking%20away%20retired%20hurt%20and%20having%20Rinku%20walk%20on%20the%20crease%20to%20be%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20at%20the%20final%20ball%2C%20needing%20two%20runs.%20Only%20one%20run%20could%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20super%20over%2C%20Rohit%20hit%20a%20four%20and%20six%20but%20India%20lost%20both%20their%20wickets%20with%20a%20ball%20to%20go%2C%20giving%20Afghanistan%2012%20runs%20to%20make.%20But%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20delivering%20this%20Super%20Over%20got%20Nabi%20and%20Gurbaz%20within%20the%20first%20three%20balls%2C%20with%20just%20one%20run%20on%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20the%20match%20and%20series%203-0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20walked%20away%20with%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%2