0does%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20so%20much%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fpictures%2Fiowa-caucus-gripped-by-bone-chilling-temperatures-2024-01-15%2F%5C%22%3Ewin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20margin%20of%20his%20success%20which%20matters.%20Trump%20is%20now%20almost%20certain%20to%20be%20the%20Republican%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20in%20November%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election.%20And%20the%20prospect%20of%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20fanciful%20notion%2C%20but%20a%2050%3A50%20possibility%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20many%20neutral%20observers%20believe%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20favourite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20247px)%2085vw%2C%20247px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22247%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20stay%20in%20the%20snowbound%20mid-West%20for%20a%20moment.%20Iowa%20is%20about%20as%20untypical%20a%20state%20as%20you%20can%20come%20across%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20It%E2%80%99s%20large%2C%20rural%2C%20overwhelmingly%20white%20and%20distinctly%20conservative.%20Pigs%20outnumber%20people%20there%20by%20seven-to-one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIowa%20is%20unusual%20among%20American%20states%20in%20having%20not%20simply%20a%20primary%20election%20to%20help%20determine%20who%20stands%20in%20November%20but%20a%20caucus.%20Only%20Republican%20supporters%20can%20take%20part.%20And%20they%20have%20to%20turn-up%20at%20a%20local%20get-together%2C%20held%20at%20a%20school%20or%20library%2C%20and%20listen%20to%20arguments%20put%20forward%20by%20supporters%20of%20the%20various%20candidates%20before%20casting%20a%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20turn%20up%20late%2C%20or%20don%E2%80%99t%20stay%20until%20the%20end%2C%20your%20choice%20might%20not%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIowa%20accounts%20for%20not%20quite%201%25%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20population%3B%20and%20only%20one-in-thirty%20Iowans%20took%20part%20in%20the%20Republican%20caucus.%20So%20not%20quite%20100%2C000%20Iowans%20are%20making%20the%20weather%20in%20a%20contest%20to%20decide%20who%20governs%20a%20nation%20of%20more%20than%20330%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20Iowa%20are%20used%20to%20harsh%20winters%2C%20but%20the%20white-out%20which%20descended%20on%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20was%20something%20different%20%E2%80%93%20pushing%20temperatures%20down%20to%20ten%20degrees%20below%20zero%20(much%20lower%20when%20wind%20chill%20is%20taken%20into%20account).%20No%20wonder%20that%20turn-out%20was%20lower%20than%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESnow%20piles%20taller%20than%20people%20in%20Ankeny%2C%20Iowa%20on%20caucus%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbkfEchH5cl%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbkfEchH5cl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jill%20Colvin%20(%40colvinj)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcolvinj%2Fstatus%2F1746981545250877505%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20American%20politics%20is%20entering%20a%20new%20Ice%20Age.%20It%E2%80%99s%20frozen%20in%20the%20past.%20Donald%20Trump%20seems%20set%20to%20be%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20a%20third%20successive%20presidential%20election%3B%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20says%20he%20is%20determined%20to%20stand%20again%20in%20spite%20of%20his%20age%20(he%E2%80%99s%2081)%2C%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Democratic%20ticket%2C%20as%20presidential%20or%20vice-presidential%20contender%2C%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20five%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20renew%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20tipped%20to%20win%20handsomely%20in%20Iowa%2C%20but%20taking%20more%20than%20half%20the%20total%20vote%20in%20the%20caucus%20is%20an%20emphatic%20triumph.%20His%20two%20main%20challengers%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67989135%5C%22%3ERon%20DeSantis%20took%20second%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20narrowly%20ahead%20of%20Nikki%20Haley%20(born%20Nimrata%20Randhawa%20to%20Punjabi%20parents%20who%20emigrated%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%201960s)%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not%20only%20a%20long%20way%20behind%2C%20but%20destined%20to%20continue%20sniping%20at%20each%20other%20to%20secure%20the%20mantle%20of%20principal%20challenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20a%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20whose%20parents%20were%20migrants%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Kerala%2C%20came%20a%20poor%20fourth%20in%20the%20caucus%20and%20has%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20He%20has%20endorsed%20his%20fellow%20conservative%2C%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20battleground%20now%20shifts%20to%20the%20much%20more%20liberal%20state%20of%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20Republican%20primary%20election%20next%20week.%20Trump%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20as%20well%20here%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20now%20has%20the%20all-important%20momentum%20which%20will%20very%20probably%20allow%20him%20to%20shake%20off%20all%20his%20challengers%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-us-enters-election-year-will-there-be-a-peaceful-transfer-of-power%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20US%20Enters%20Election%20Year%2C%20Will%20There%20Be%20a%20Peaceful%20Transfer%20of%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20could%2C%20of%20course%2C%20still%20disrupt%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20plans%20to%20run.%20He%20faces%20a%20slew%20of%20legal%20cases%2C%20several%20arising%20out%20of%20his%20refusal%20to%20accept%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20last%20presidential%20election%20and%20the%20storming%20of%20the%20Congress%20building%20by%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20evidence%20from%20Iowa%20is%20that%20the%20more%20legal%20cases%20against%20Trump%2C%20the%20more%20Republicans%20support%20him%2C%20apparently%20convinced%20that%20the%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democrats%2C%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20officially%20start%20their%20primary%20elections%20until%20the%20contest%20in%20South%20Carolina%20on%20February%203.%20But%20the%20process%20is%20a%20formality.%20No%20candidate%20of%20substance%20is%20standing%20against%20the%20incumbent%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20simply%20a%20pity%2C%20but%20close%20to%20a%20tragedy.%20Biden%20is%20an%20unpopular%20president%2C%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20seen%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20unfairly%20%E2%80%93%20not%20to%20have%20been%20a%20good%20steward%20of%20the%20economy.%20And%20his%20advanced%20age%20is%20evident%20in%20his%20stiffness%20when%20walking%20and%20in%20moments%20of%20apparent%20confusion.%20Most%20Americans%2C%20opinion%20polls%20suggest%2C%20think%20Biden%20is%20too%20old%20to%20serve%20as%20president%20for%20another%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20seems%20to%20have%20convinced%20himself%20that%20only%20he%20can%20frustrate%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20ambition%20to%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20Democrats%20believe%20that%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%20could%20imperil%20America%E2%8