n-charles-rivkin-contract-ceo-1235875897%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fog%20disrupts%20flight%20operations%20at%20Delhi%20airport%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705543561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106941599%2Cimgsize-8256.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Ffog-disrupts-flight-operations-at-delhi-airport-imd-issues-yellow-alert%2Farticleshow%2F106941587.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Ffog-disrupts-flight-operations-at-delhi-airport-imd-issues-yellow-alert%2Farticleshow%2F106941587.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%207%2C500%20Employees%20Laid%20Off%20By%20Tech%20Giants%20So%20Far%20In%20January%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech's%20%26quot%3BYear%20of%20Efficiency%26quot%3B%20may%20be%20over%20but%20recent%20layoffs%20at%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20have%20signaled%20the%20firms%20will%20keep%20cutting%20jobs%20in%202024%20as%20they%20make%20big%20investments%20in%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20and%20industry%20experts%20believe%20the%20layoffs%20would%20be%20smaller%20and%20more%20targeted%20this%20year%2C%20with%20firms%20that%20are%20racing%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20more%20likely%20to%20make%20such%20moves%20to%20offset%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20they%20are%20spending%20on%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlphabet%20suggested%20that%20last%20week%2C%20saying%20it%20plans%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20priorities%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Google%20parent%20laid%20off%20around%20a%20thousand%20employees%20across%20multiple%20divisions%2C%20including%20in%20its%20voice%20assistant%20unit%20and%20team%20responsible%20for%20Pixel%20and%20Fitbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20its%20advertising%20business%20was%20not%20spared%2C%20with%20a%20report%20on%20Tuesday%20saying%20that%20hundreds%20of%20jobs%20were%20being%20cut%20at%20the%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon.com%20laid%20off%20several%20hundred%20employees%20in%20its%20streaming%20and%20studio%20operations%20last%20week.%20Hundreds%20of%20jobs%20were%20also%20cut%20in%20its%20Twitch%20live-streaming%20platform%20and%20Audible%20audiobook%20unit%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20tech%20firms%20have%20let%20go%20more%20than%207%2C500%20employees%20so%20far%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20tracking%20website%20Layoffs.fyi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20company%20wants%20to%20get%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20AI%20revolution%20and%20they%20are%20all%20making%20sure%20they%20have%20these%20capabilities%20and%20are%20prioritizing%20them%2C%20even%20when%20it%20is%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20other%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20D.A.%20Davidson%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20analyst%20Gil%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20are%20aggressively%20investing%20in%20their%20AI%20efforts.%20Google%2C%20which%20is%20trying%20to%20close%20the%20gap%20with%20Microsoft%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20last%20month%20unveiled%20its%20long-awaited%20Gemini%20model%2C%20while%20Amazon%20is%20developing%20a%20model%20codenamed%20%26quot%3BOlympus%26quot%3B%20to%20compete%20with%20ChatGPT-maker%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHIRING%20PRIORITIES%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20total%20size%20of%20the%20layoffs%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20much%20smaller%2C%20compared%20with%20last%20year's%20massive%20cuts%2C%20as%20tech%20spending%20picks%20up%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20more%20stable%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20sector%20shed%20168%2C032%20jobs%20in%202023%20and%20accounted%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20layoffs%20across%20industries%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Challenger%2C%20Gray%2