%20for%20AI%3F'%20I%20am%20pessimistic%2C%20but%20many%20smart%20people%20believe%20it%20will%20be%20much%20shorter%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705543560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5k4e24dg_google-generic_625x300_18_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-7-500-employees-laid-off-by-tech-giants-so-far-in-january-report-4875238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20Tech's%20%26quot%3BYear%20of%20Efficiency%26quot%3B%20may%20be%20over%20but%20recent%20layoffs%20at%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20have%20signaled%20the%20firms%20will%20keep%20cutting%20jobs%20in%202024%20as%20they%20make%20big%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-7-500-employees-laid-off-by-tech-giants-so-far-in-january-report-4875238%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-7-500-employees-laid-off-by-tech-giants-so-far-in-january-report-4875238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-7-500-employees-laid-off-by-tech-giants-so-far-in-january-report-4875238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRed%20Sea%20Matter%20Of%20Concern%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Hardeep%20Puri%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20risk%20in%20navigating%20the%20maritime%20routes%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20enough%20wisdom%20around%26quot%3B%20to%20not%20allow%20the%20situation%20to%20escalate%2C%20Union%20minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20has%20told%20NDTV%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20meet%20at%20Davos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20state%20players%20involved%20want%20the%20situation%20to%20escalate%20and%20allow%20hostilities%20on%20a%20bigger%20scale%2C%20he%20said%20weeks%20after%20a%20merchant%20ship%2C%20Chem%20Pluto%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20drone%20400%20km%20of%20the%20Indian%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20attempt%20to%20cause%20uncertainty%20even%20of%20perception%20in%20any%20sea%20route%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20is%20enough%20maturity%20and%20wisdom%20around%20to%20be%20able%20to%20navigate%20around%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20why%20there%20is%20this%20sudden%20outbreak%20of%20violence%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20some%20of%20the%20players%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20ready%20for%20the%20vast%20changes%26quot%3B%20that%20happened%20in%20a%20short%20while.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20introspection%20is%20done%20and%20I%20am%20cautiously%20optimistic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20months%2C%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebel%20group%20has%20been%20stepping%20up%20its%20attack%20on%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20lane%20in%20retaliation%20to%20Israel's%20air%20strikes%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%2C%20though%2C%20was%20struck%20while%20passing%20Iran%20--%20the%20obvious%20conclusion%20from%20the%20situation%20has%20been%20vehemently%20denied%20by%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%20-%20carrying%2021%20crew%20members%20(20%20Indians%20and%201%20Vietnamese)%20-was%20struck%20by%20a%20drone%20400%20km%20of%20the%20Indian%20coastline%20in%20late%20December.%20Following%20it%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20stationed%20several%20warships%20and%20long-range%20maritime%20reconnaissance%20aircraft%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Puri%20said%20discussions%20are%20taking%20place%20with%20Iran%20and%20others.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20even%20the%20foreign%20minister%20was%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Teheran%2C%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20slammed%20the%20attacks%20on%20ships%20by%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20concern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20different%20note%2C%20asked%20about%20India's%20transition%20to%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%20it%20would%20take%20less%20time%20than%20previously%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20energy%20atmanirbharta%20(self-reliance)%20by%202047.%20I%20think%20it%20can%20be%20done%20by%202037%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20a%20few%20things%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDomestic%20exploration%20is%20becoming%20much%20more%20focussed%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20transitioning%20on%20biofuels%20has%20been%20a%20very%20impressive%20story.%20The%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20global%20biofuels%20alliance%20will%20help%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705543380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2mmrv2po_hardeep-singh-puri-ndtv_625x300_18_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fred-sea-matter-of-concern-but-hardeep-singh-puri-to-ndtv-4883674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sudden%20risk%20in%20navigating%20the%20maritime%20routes%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20enough%20wisdom%20around%26quot%3B%20to%20not%20allow%20the%20situation%20to%20escalate%2C%20Union%20minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20has%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fred-sea-matter-of-concern-but-hardeep-singh-puri-to-ndtv-4883674%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.c