for%20short%20bursts%20of%20time%20because%20she%20made%20the%20Drop%20through%20a%20gate%2C%20where%20Vanir%20drop%20their%20power%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6504a1c04afd900019c0081f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20her%20Starborn%20abilities%2C%20Bryce%20became%20a%20portal%20after%20her%20friend%20Danika%20Fendyr%20(more%20on%20her%20in%20a%20bit)%20inked%20Luna's%20Horn%2C%20a%20magical%20object%20that%20creates%20portals%2C%20onto%20her%20back%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20travel%20between%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20meets%20her%20mate%20Orion%20(Hunt)%20Athalar%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20they%20don't%20recognize%20themselves%20as%20such%20until%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%20Hunt%20is%20an%20angel%2C%20a%20species%20formally%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20Malakh%20on%20Midgard.%20Hunt%20can%20fly%20thanks%20to%20his%20wings%2C%20and%20he%20has%20power%20over%20lightning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHunt%20was%20previously%20a%20slave%20owned%20by%20the%20republic%20as%20punishment%20for%20rebelling%20against%20them%2C%20but%20he%20was%20freed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20still%20works%20for%20the%2033rd%20Legion%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20triarii%2C%20the%20private%20protection%20for%20the%20governor%20of%20Crescent%20City%2C%20who%20is%20always%20an%20archangel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%2C%26quot%3B%20Ruhn%20and%20Hunt%20help%20Bryce%20escape%20to%20another%20world%20to%20save%20their%20planet%20from%20the%20Asteri%2C%20evil%20creatures%20who%20have%20been%20leeching%20power%20from%20its%20citizens%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBryce's%20late%20friend%20Danika%20Fendyr%20and%20her%20Pack%20of%20Devils%20move%20the%20plot%20along%20despite%20dying%20in%20the%20first%20book%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20met%20her%20best%20friend%20Danika%20Fendyr%20at%20college%2C%20and%20they%20were%20attached%20at%20the%20hip%20until%20Danika%20died%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%20Danika%20was%20a%20powerful%20wolf%20shifter%2C%20the%20Alpha%20of%20the%20Pack%20of%20Devils%2C%20and%20the%20heir%20apparent%20to%20the%20Valbaran%20wolves.%20She%20was%20also%20a%20bloodhound%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20sniff%20people's%20bloodlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20quietly%20to%20undermine%20the%20Asteri%20until%20her%20death%2C%20tattooing%20the%20horn%20on%20Bryce's%20back%20and%20partnering%20with%20a%20human%20named%20Sofie%20Renast%20to%20uncover%20how%20the%20Asteri%20came%20to%20Midgard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a84f32dcdb354a98586b6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223039%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20her%20death%2C%20she%20also%20secretly%20mated%20the%20angel%20Baxian%20Argos%2C%20known%20to%20most%20as%20the%20Helhound%2C%20and%20left%20a%20luxury%20apartment%20to%20Bryce%20in%20her%20will%2C%20where%20she%20kept%20clues%20about%20her%20rebellious%20activities.%20Baxian%20tried%20to%20help%20Bryce%20and%20Hunt%20throughout%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Asteri%20took%20him%20prisoner%20alongside%20Ruhn%20and%20Hunt%20