lUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fpli-scheme-spurs-rs-1-03-trillion-investment-boosts-exports-jobs-124011700826_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fpli-scheme-spurs-rs-1-03-trillion-investment-boosts-exports-jobs-124011700826_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fpli-scheme-spurs-rs-1-03-trillion-investment-boosts-exports-jobs-124011700826_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Time%20For%20Platforms%20To%20Take%20Responsibility%3A%20Minister%20To%20NDTV%20On%20Deepfakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20aspects%20to%20new%20technology%20-%20There%20will%20be%20transitions%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20productivity.%20Several%20complex%20challenges%20like%20climate%20change%2C%20drug%20discovery%2C%20disease%20detection%2C%20and%20agriculture%20can%20be%20solved%20but%20there%20will%20be%20negatives%20too%20and%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20harness%20the%20positive%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20NDTV%20while%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20related%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20summit%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20said%20the%20regulation%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20is%20an%20important%20issue%20and%20there%20are%20global%20concerns.%20The%20Union%20Minister%20put%20forward%20his%20viewpoint%20on%20the%20regulation%20of%20AI%20amid%20growing%20incidents%20of%20deepfakes%20circulated%20targeting%20celebrities%2C%20a%20concern%20raised%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20well%2C%20who%20termed%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bchallenge%20to%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20concerns%20about%20copyright%2C%20identity%20theft%2C%20deepfakes%20and%20racial%20bias%20and%20we%20are%20part%20of%20the%20global%20thinking%20process%20on%20AI%20and%20our%20approach%20of%20innovation%20and%20regulation%20has%20been%20widely%20appreciated%20and%20acknowledged%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20backed%20the%20proposition%20of%20regulation%20and%20to%20ensure%20social%20media%20platforms%20are%20brought%20into%20the%20framework%20of%20regulation%20and%20accountability%20to%20counter%20deepfakes%20and%20harmful%20AI-generated%20content.%20The%20minister%20underpinned%20the%20proposition%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20steps%20the%20Centre%20is%20taking%20to%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20things%20are%20being%20done%20within%20the%20IT%20Act%20rules%20under%20there%20are%20provisions%20under%20it%20to%20prevent%20misuse%20of%20AI%20we've%20had%20workshops%20with%20the%20platforms%20and%20people%20from%20the%20industry%20but%20I%20think%20they%20need%20to%20do%20more%20than%20this%20and%20deploy%20technology%20to%20detect%20deepfakes.%20The%20time%20has%20come%20for%20platforms%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20they%20are%20publishing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20called%20an%20urgent%20action%20to%20combat%20deepfakes%20and%20said%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20a%20bigger%20role%20and%20they%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20delay%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20is%20hopeful%20that%20the%20Digital%20India%20Bill%20is%20passed%20when%20the%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20Minister%20visited%20the%20Swiss%20Rail%20Control%20Centre%20and%20said%20they%20are%20excited%20about%20the%20growth%20of%20railways%20in%20India%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20construction.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20Kavach%20system%2C%20an%20automatic%20train%20protection%20system%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20world%20moved%20to%20automatic%20train%20protection%20in%20the%201990s%20but%20the%20governments%20at%20that%20time%20were%20not%20interested%20in%20bringing%20in%20new%20technology.%20In%202016%2C%20we%20had%20the%20system%20approved%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20meticulous%20process.%20We%20did%20trials%20in%20the%20same%20year%20and%20in%202019%20we%20got%20the%20certification%20and%20now%20we%20implementing%20it%20for%201%2C500%20km%20and%20later%20it%20will%20be%20extended%20to%206%2C500%20km.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20spoke%20about%20semiconductors%20and%20the%20global%20concern%20surrounding%20the%20supply%20chain.%20The%20minister%20said%20%26quot%3BSemiconductors%20are%20the%20foundational%20technology%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%20needs%20them.%20People%20are%20happy%20with%20India's%20entry%20into%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%20People%20appreciate%20India's%20focus%20on%20talent%2C%20innovation%20and%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20supply%20of%20semiconductors%20is%20regulated%2C%20with%20very%20few%20countries%20manufacturing%20it%20creating%20a%20high%20demand%20in%20the%20global%20market%20amid%20geopolitical%20standoffs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20we%20are%20developing%20a%20comprehensive%20semiconductor%20ecosystem%20to%20address%20the%20demands%20and%20industry%20leaders%20have%20said%20this%20is%20the%20time%20to%20take%20the%20next%20leap%20like%20starting%20projects%20to%20design%20chips%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20products%20and%20it%20will%20help%20India%20supply%20them%20and%20given%20the%20geopolitical%20constraints%20regarding%20semiconductors%2C%20the%20trust%20on%20PM%20Modi%20comes%20into%20the%20picture%20and%20his%20work%20in%20the%20foreign%20policy%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705516380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fuof87om_ashwini-vaishnaw-davos_625x300_17_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftime-for-platforms-to-take-responsibility-minister-ashwini-vaishnaw-to-ndtv-on-deepfak