A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-eyes-100-bn-annual-fdi-in-coming-years-it-minister-vaishnaw-124011700904_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Prodigy%20Went%20to%20MIT%20at%2014%2C%20Has%20Now%20Built%20One%20of%20World%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Advanced%20Air%20Purification%20Tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F9936%2Fangad-inventor-child-prodigy-ted-talk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAngad%20Daryani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2025-year-old%20founder%20of%20Praan%2C%20Inc.%2C%20a%20deep-tech%20startup%20based%20out%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20generation%20that%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20reality%20of%20a%20bleak%20future%E2%80%94one%20plagued%20with%20pollution%20and%20climate%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrevious%20generations%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20an%20exciting%20future%20where%20If%20you%20worked%20hard%20and%20built%20a%20career%2C%20%5Bthe%20expectation%20was%20that%5D%20the%20future%20would%20be%20great.%20But%20our%20generation%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20animal%20extinction%2C%20and%20severe%20air%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F201010%2Findia-water-pollution-cleaning-complaints-robot-hair-innovation-hair-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20I%20was%20about%20six%20years%20old%20and%20learned%20about%20these%20things%20on%20National%20Geographic%2C%20this%20discomfort%20about%20a%20bleak%20future%20has%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Angad%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolving%20real-world%20problems%20has%20always%20excited%20him.%20A%20child%20prodigy%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Angad%20built%20his%20first%20robot%20and%20a%20solar-powered%20boat%20at%20age%208%2C%20besides%20building%20a%20homegrown%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303783%2Fchennai-startup-avay-biosciences-builds-bio-3d-printer-to-print-human-tissues%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3D%20printer%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2013%20and%20an%20e-reader%20(Virtual%20Brailler)%20for%20the%20visually-challenged%20by%2015.%20He%20briefly%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20schooling%20system%20because%20of%20his%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20rote%20learning-based%20state%20board%20system.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20school%20confusing.%20While%20I%20was%20doing%20well%20academically%2C%20the%20rote-based%20education%20didn%E2%80%99t%20build%20my%20fundamentals%20which%20would%20become%20obvious%20when%20I%E2%80%99d%20compete%20in%20Olympiads%20and%20struggle%20to%20solve%20problems.%20At%20the%20same%20time%20as%20a%20hobby%2C%20I%20was%20building%20all%20these%20complex%20engineering%20projects%20at%20home%20on%20my%20own%20simply%20by%20watching%20videos%20or%20reading%20books.%20When%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%2C%20my%20parents%20hired%20a%20tutor%20who%20would%20teach%20me%20all%20the%20same%20things%20as%20other%20high%20school%20students%2C%20while%20rebuilding%20my%20fundamentals.%20Since%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20homework%20and%20was%20solving%20problems%20while%20learning%20the%20topics%2C%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20scientific%20hobbies.%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20when%20Angad%20was%20around%2014%20years%20old%2C%20he%20wrote%20an%20email%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsolve.mit.edu%2Fchallenges%2Felevateprize%2Fsolutions%2F29235%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Professor%20Ramesh%20Raskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Indian-born%20professor%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT).%20Currently%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20media%20arts%20and%20sciences%20at%20the%20renowned%20MIT%20Media%20Lab%20and%20an%20advisor%20to%20renowned%20technology%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20amusing%20looking%20back%20at%20my%20ignorance%2C%20but%20I%20wrote%20to%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20are%20an%20Indian%20professor%20and%20MIT%20brings%20bright%20young%20students%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20its%20campus%2C%20so%20why%20not%20bring%20on%20someone%20from%20India%3F%E2%80%99%20Incredibly%2C%20he%20wrote%20back%20almost%20immediately%20and%20I%20ended%20up%20working%20with%20MIT%20via%20their%20India%20Initiative%20for%20two%20years%20building%20technology%20that%20could%20solve%20real-world%20problems%20in%20health%20tech.%20Even%20till%20this%20day%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1204696763436090%5C%22%3E%20Professor%20Raskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20supportive%20of%20my%20journey%20and%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20mentor%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20those%20two%20years%20working%20with%20MIT%2C%20he%20went%20back%20to%20an%20IB%20(International%20Baccalaureate)%20school%2C%20following%20which%20he%20studied%20electrical%20engineering%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Georgia%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(Georgia%20Tech).%20It%20was%20during%20his%20time%20in%20college%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20act%20on%20the%20growing%20problem%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20began%20developing%20solutions%20for%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20startup%20has%20built%20one%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworld%E2%80%99s%20most%20advanced%20air%20purification%20technologies%E2%80%9D%20using%20a%20unique%20combination%20of%20electrical%20charge%20dispersion%20and%20airflow%20optimization-based%20processes%20%E2%80%93%20allowing%20particles%20to%20be%20charged%20and%20creating%20electric%20fields%20that%20move%20the%20particles%20to%20a%20collection%20chamber.%20Angad%20combined%20his%20background%20in%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20product%20design%2C%20IoT%2C%20process%20engineering%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20to%20create%20a%20whole%20new%20class%20of%20air%20purifiers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20his%20solution%20works%20through%20a%20network%20of%20air%20purifying%20units%20that%20can%20clean%20air%20within%20large%20spaces%20like%20factory%20floors%20in%20just%20minutes%20by%20mapping%20how%20the%20pollution%20is%20flowing%20on%20the%20shop%20floor%20and%20then%20strategically%20placing%20the%20air%20purifiers%20to%20capture%20that%20pollution.%20For%20example%2C%20Praan%E2%80%99s%20latest%20product%20called%20the%20MK%20II%20(%E2%80%98Mach%202%E2%80%99)%20has%20a%20high%20purification%20rate%20of%201300%20cubic%20feet%20per%20minute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MK%20II%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-3-1705505138-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338473%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20MK%20II%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspired%20by%20illness%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Angad%20suffered%20from%20asthma.%20Every%20winter%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20he%20would%20endure%20breathing%20difficulties%20due%20to%20high%20air%20pollution%20and%20his%20family%20would%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20city.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20asthma%20and%20high%20dust%20levels%20in%20the%20city%2C%20I%20would%20struggle%20to%20play%20football.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20run%20properly%20because%20my%20stamina%20would%20take%20a%20hit%20and%20I%20would%20cough%20constantly.%20But%20this%20was%20a%20reality%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20living%20around%20me.%20Today%2C%20while%20I%20can%20move%20to%20a%20country%20with%20a%20cleaner%20environment%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20them%20breathe%20this%20toxic%20air%20every%20day%20and%20this%20is%20why%20finding%20a%20solution%20was%20so%20important%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Angad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20just%20before%20he%20began%20his%20sophomore%20year%20at%20Georgia%20Tech%2C%20he%20began%20working%20on%20solutions%20for%20urban%20air%20pollution%20but%20this%20came%20with%20some%20real%20challenges.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20used%20Georgia%20Tech%E2%80%99s%20infrastructure%20to%20build%20my%20solution%2C%20as%20per%20the%20clauses%2C%20they%20would%20own%20all%20the%20intellectual%20property.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20commercialise%20it%20as%20per%20evolving%20requirements.%20And%20hence%2C%20commercially%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20any%20of%20their%20labs.%20Also%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20my%20visa%20status%2C%20I%20legally%20could%20not%20register%20a%20company%20and%20start%20a%20business%20with%20a%20co-founder%20there%20while%20being%20a%20college%20student%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20the%20truth%20about%20building%20air%20purification%20technology%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20purifier%20or%20the%20sensor%20you%E2%80%99re%20building%2C%20but%20you%E2%80%99re%20also%20building%20the%20infrastructure%20to%20test%20it%20in%20different%20wind%2C%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20pollution%20conditions.%20Given%20the%20lack%20of%20financial%20resources%20during%20the%20bootstrap%20phase%2C%20it%20was%20pretty%20hard%20to%20build%20a%20safe%20test%20chamber%20that%20could%20work%20in%20all%20these%20different%20conditions%2C%20provide%20accurate%20and%20reliable%20data%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20test%20with%20all%20different%20materials%20of%20dust%2C%20gases%20and%20pollutants%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Angad.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Angad%20started%20building%20the%20prototypes%20of%20these%20filterless%20purification%20systems%20based%20on%20physics%20principles%20out%20of%20his%20apartment%20room%20near%20Georgia%20Tech%20where%20basic%20characteristics%20could%20be%20inspected%20visually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpraan.io%2Fnews%2Fpraans-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20this%20detailed%20description%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Praan%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20carry%20the%20prototype%20for%202%20miles%20several%20times%20every%20week%20from%20his%20apartment%20to%20the%20on-campus%20makerspace%20to%20build%20the%20earliest%20versions%20of%20a%20filterless%20air%20purification%20system.%20The%20device%20first%20started%20with%20a%20paint-bucket%20prototype%20and%20then%20made%20it%20to%20a%20steel%20ducting%20system%20version.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20continued%20to%20work%20on%20it%2C%20more%20and%20more%20students%20around%20campus%20would%20find%20him%20walking%20across%20the%20lawn%20with%20this%205ft-tall%20metal%20structure%20which%20looked%20like%20a%20jet%20engine.%20Out%20of%20curiosity%2C%20they%20would%20talk%20to%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20weeks%20later%2C%20however%2C%20CNN%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20to%20interview%20for%20their%20%E2%80%98Tomorrow%E2%80%99s%20Hero%E2%80%99%20series.%20Following%20discussions%20over%20email%2C%20they%20came%20down%20to%20the%20Georgia%20Tech%20campus%20and%20shot%20a%20video%20with%20him%20where%20they%20discussed%20his%20mission%2C%20approach%20and%20the%20technology%20he%20was%20building%20to%20address%20urban%20air%20pollution.%20CNN%20eventually%20recorded%20and%20published%20this%20article%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Ftv%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2Ftomorrows-hero-angad-daryani.cnn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20went%20viral%20in%20no%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Angad%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20initially%20interested%20in%20building%20your%20conventional%20indoor%20air%20purifiers%20that%20you%20can%20install%20at%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20commercial%20appeal%2C%20I%20resisted%20developing%20a%20conventional%20indoor%20air%20purifying%20system.%20I%20was%20not%20thinking%20about%20the%20top%201%25%20who%20can%20afford%20a%20Dyson%20but%20that%20child%20who%20walks%20to%20school%20every%20day%20or%20a%20factory%20worker%20breathing%20in%20toxic%20air%20during%20his%2Fher%20shifts.%20My%20objective%20was%20to%20find%20something%20that%20can%20be%20done%20for%20large%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20important%20facet%20was%20not%20to%20involve%20filters.%20If%20I%20keep%20a%20filter-based%20air%20purifier%20at%20a%20large%20space%20in%20Delhi%20during%20the%20winter%20one%20would%20have%20to%20change%20the%20filter%20every%20hour.%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20filterless%20system%2C%20which%20means%20no%20recurring%20cost%20of%20ownership%20in%20these%20large%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angad%20Daryani%20with%20an%20MK%20II%20at%20a%20factory%20floor.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FPraan.io-Image-1-1705504986-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338472%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAngad%20Daryani%20with%20an%20MK%20II%20at%20a%20factory%20floor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPower%20of%20volunteers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20after%20his%20appearance%20on%20CNN%2C%20Angad%20returned%20to%20India%20for%20the%20summer%20where%20he%20continued%20to%20work%20on%20prototyping%20the%20devices%20and%20testing%20them%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpraan.io%2Fnews%2Fpraans-story%2F%5C%22%3E%20the%20Praan%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20this%20project%20was%20entirely%20bootstrapped%20with%20no%20external%20financing%2C%20all%20the%20prototyping%20was%20done%20with%20off-the-shelf%20components%20and%20built-in%20Angad%E2%80%99s%20bedroom%20and%20terrace%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20each%20prototype%20was%20hand%20built%2C%20cut%2C%20glued%2C%20soldered%2C%20and%20tested%20outdoors.%20During%20this%20process%2C%20he%20kept%20posting%20pictures%20of%20his%20progress%20on%20the%20internet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explanation%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246668%2Fenergy-saving-building-management-system-bios-enlite-research-garima-bharadwaj-gaurav-bali-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeeptech%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20still%20new%20in%20India%20and%20hence%20the%20availability%20of%20risk%20capital%20was%20bleak.%20So%20Angad%20had%20to%20bootstrap%20the%20project%20and%20saw%2030%20more%20volunteers%20join%20him%20in%20his%20mission%20as%20he%20returned%20to%20Atlanta%20in%20the%20Fall%202018.%20This%20team%20was%20fundamentally%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20filterless%20air%20purification%20using%20cold%20plasma%20technology%20was%20possible%20and%20was%20alternatively%20also%20experimenting%20with%20bioengineering%20techniques%20for%20purifying%20air%20in%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20team%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20an%20office%20or%20access%20to%20capital%2C%20all%20experimenting%20of%20the%20core%20tech%20was%20done%20in%20public%20parking%20lots%20or%20park%20benches%20in%20Atlanta%20during%20after-hours%20or%20on%20weekends.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20Angad%20and%20his%20team%20of%20over%2030%20volunteers%20developed%20the%20first%20prototypes%20for%20filterless%20air%20purification%20devices%20and%20learned%20how%20to%20design%20test%20rigs%20for%20building%20these%20systems%20%E2%80%93%20a%20process%20they%20say%20they%20continue%20to%20invent%20and%20learn%20from%20even%20today%2C%206%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20the%20project%20got%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Praan%E2%80%99.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20Angad%20and%20a%20few%20members%20of%20the%20team%20even%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20in%20India%20to%20propose%20a%20filterless%20approach%20to%20outdoor%20air%20purification.%20Following%20this%2C%20in%20December%202018%2C%20they%20flew%20to%20New%20Delhi%20and%20demonstrated%20the%20concept%20for%20their%20first%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%20this%2C%20the%20conversations%20around%20Praan%E2%80%99s%20mission%20grew%20within%20the%20Georgia%20Tech%20and%20Emory%20University%20Campuses%2C%20leading%20to%20many%20more%20people%20applying%20to%20join%20the%20team%20of%20volunteers%20working%20on%20this%20mission.%20In%20a%20fraction%20of%20weeks%2C%20the%20team%20grew%20to%2064%20people%20in%20the%20Spring%202019.%20This%20was%20the%20largest%20volunteering%20team%20%5Bthat%5D%20Praan%20ever%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20the%20Praan%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20develop%20filterless%20large%20space%20air%20purification%20technology%2C%20you%20need%20persons%20with%20different%20specialisations%E2%80%94mechanical%20designers%2C%20chemical%20engineers%2C%20physicists%2C%20full-stack%20developers%20and%20those%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20power%20electronics%20and%20embedded%20hardware%2C%20among%20others.%20When%20I%20started%20developing%20this%20technology%20in%20my%20sophomore%20year%2C%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20prototypes%20but%20knew%20nothing%20about%20fluid%20dynamics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angad%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lot%20of%20painstaking%20work%20into%20developing%20Praan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338475%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20lot%20of%20painstaking%20work%20into%20developing%20Praan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20entice%20student%20volunteers%20to%20work%20on%20your%20project%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20give%20them%20recognition%20on%20patents%2C%20which%20is%20very%20valuable%20for%20a%20third%20or%20fourth-year%20engineering%20student.%20And%20if%20you%20can%20give%20them%20real%20hands-on%20skills%2C%20which%20they%20are%20practising%20through%20that%20semester%2C%20they%20have%20a%20good%20story%20to%20tell%20to%20job%20recruiters.%20Plus%2C%20given%20my%20prior%20experience%20at%20MIT%20and%20the%20network%20I%20developed%20there%2C%20I%20knew%20senior%20people%20who%20worked%20in%20companies%20like%20Apple%2C%20Tesla%20or%20SpaceX.%20I%20could%20help%20introduce%20these%20volunteers%20to%20these%20people%2C%20saying%20they%20worked%20on%20my%20project.%20For%20example%2C%20Patrick%20Finley%2C%20the%20founder%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flanderchallenge.space%2Fteam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Lander%20Challenger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20to%20work%20at%20SpaceX%20after%20working%20as%20a%20volunteer%20for%20Praan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20summer%2C%20Angad%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20one%20of%20his%20Teaching%20Assistants%20(TAs)%20and%20ran%20further%20experiments%20at%20a%20store%20room%20belonging%20to%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20company.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Naresh%20Shahani%20(currently%20a%20director%20at%20Praan)%2C%20helped%20obtain%20an%20unsecured%20loan%20of%20%2415%2C000%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20and%20development.%20Taken%20in%20Angad%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20this%20sum%20was%20eventually%20doubled%20and%20returned%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20summer%2C%20Angad%2C%20his%20TA%20and%20two%20interns%20put%20together%20the%20prototype%20of%20what%20would%20become%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20Purifier.%20The%20plan%20moving%20forward%20was%20that%20Angad%20would%20graduate%20in%202020%2C%20run%20this%20company%20full-time%20after%20graduating%2C%20and%20raise%20capital.%20Despite%20his%20best%20efforts%2C%20securing%20funding%20was%20a%20major%20challenge.%20By%20January%202020%2C%20investors%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20caught%20on%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20deep%20tech%20and%20the%20offers%20on%20the%20table%20were%20not%20satisfactory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20he%20managed%20%E2%80%9Cto%20pool%20together%20some%20soft%20commitments%20worth%20%241.35M%20from%20an%20Indian%20VC%20fund%20and%20a%20few%20strategic%20angels%20on%20very%20bad%20investment%20terms%E2%80%9D.%20As%20these%20deals%20were%20being%20finalised%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%20and%20everything%20fell%20apart.%20Yet%20to%20graduate%20from%20college%2C%20he%20had%20to%20pack%20everything%20up%20and%20come%20back%20to%20India%20while%20completing%20online%20classes%20to%20get%20his%20degree.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20a%20silver%20lining.%20Since%20people%20were%20losing%20their%20jobs%20and%20internships%2C%20there%20were%20many%20looking%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that%20would%20advance%20their%20careers.%20Similar%20to%20what%20he%20did%20earlier%2C%20Angad%20offered%20recognition%20on%20Praan%20patents%20to%20anyone%20who%20helped%20develop%20the%20technology%20further%20either%20remotely%20or%20even%20as%20a%20volunteer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Praan%20managed%20to%20onboard%20about%2060%20volunteers%20from%20multiple%20time%20zones%20who%20chose%20to%20dedicate%20about%20four%20months%20of%20their%20time%20to%20work%20on%20their%20technology.%C2%A0%20While%20the%20hardware%20was%20built%20and%20developed%20out%20of%20Angad%20and%20his%20intern%E2%80%99s%20bedrooms%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337225%2Fvolunteer-beach-cleanup-akshat-shah-shubh-mehta-mumbai-new-year-resolution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20contributed%20with%20their%20ideas%20and%20engineering%20drawings%20for%20their%20prototypes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Praan%20website%2C%20there%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Cdesign%20teams%20working%20on%20ideas%20for%20the%20MK%20One%20product%2C%20the%20indoor%20air%20purification%2C%20bioengineering%2C%20carbon%20capture%2C%20and%20software%20engineering%20products%E2%80%94all%20without%20any%20capital%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20funding%20and%20assistance%20finally%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Emergent%20Ventures%2C%20a%20fellowship%20and%20grant%20programme%20run%20by%20famous%20economist%20Dr.%20Tyler%20Cowen.%20It%20gave%20this%20fledgling%20startup%20the%20largest%20grant%20during%20the%20lockdown%20period%20which%20helped%20them%20access%20capital%20to%20build%20prototypes%20and%20test%20rigs%20as%20well.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20they%20developed%20a%20working%20prototype%20of%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20purifier%20in%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20customer%20or%20investor%20interest%20and%20a%20negligible%20amount%20of%20vendors%20were%20willing%20to%20manufacture%20the%20MKOne%20prototype.%20Angad%20spent%20about%20five%20months%20waiting%20for%20vendors%20to%20manufacture%20the%20first%20usable%20MKOne%20prototype.%20Tired%20of%20waiting%2C%20Angad%20decided%20%E2%80%9Cto%20build%20the%20first%20MKOne%20prototype%20at%20a%20utensil%20manufacturing%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20were%20differences%20between%20this%20prototype%20and%20future%20products%20in%20terms%20of%20dimensions%20and%20finishing%2C%20they%20finally%20had%20a%20real%20product%20that%20they%20could%20show%20investors.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20gave%20the%20Praan%20team%20real%20confidence%20that%20they%20could%20start%20to%20manufacture%20this%20product%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCw2hbhUt6-l%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCw2hbhUt6-l%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20