0the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166365%2Fbhopal-cop-best-cyber-cop-award-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolice%20force%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20COVID%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20I%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20cybersecurity.%20I%20had%20also%20worked%20with%20a%20cybersecurity%20company%20previously%2C%20so%20I%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20such%20matters.%20I%20also%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20without%20a%20paid%20job%2C%20Murthy%20had%20already%20started%20exhausting%20his%20savings.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20my%20friend%20informed%20me%20about%20an%20instant%20loan%20application%20and%20installed%20it%20on%20my%20phone.%20After%20he%20installed%20the%20app%2C%20I%20instantly%20received%20Rs%206%2C000.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20use%20the%20money%20as%20I%20found%20out%20that%20it%20was%20not%20affiliated%20with%20the%20RBI%20or%20any%20other%20banks.%20They%20were%20all%20loan%20sharks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20they%20told%20me%20that%20I%20would%20be%20charged%20at%20an%2018%20percent%20rate%20of%20interest%20per%20day%20and%20I%20have%20to%20return%20the%20entire%20amount%20within%20six%20days.%20In%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20was%20called%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20person%20started%20abusing%20me%20using%20foul%20language.%20He%20also%20warned%20me%20that%20if%20I%20do%20not%20return%20the%20amount%2C%20he%20will%20share%20my%20morphed%20images%20to%20defame%20me.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20access%20to%20all%20my%20contacts%20and%20my%20gallery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%