F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-expels-iran-envoy-recalls-ambassador-from-tehran-after-air-strike%2Famp_articleshow%2F106929348.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Everything%20Is%20Dictated%20By%20the%20Times%20That%20We're%20Living%20in'%3A%20Resul%20Pookutty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17163653%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-17-at-4.35.17-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKozhikode%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%202023%2C%20Oscar-winning%20sound%20designer%20Resul%20Pookutty%20made%20his%20debut%20as%20a%20director%20with%20%3Cem%3EOtta%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20Malayalam%20film%20following%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20young%20men%20who%20run%20away%20from%20their%20homes.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20S.%20Hariharan%E2%80%99s%20book%C2%A0%3Ci%3ERunaway%20Children%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Hariharan%2C%20a%20successful%20businessman%2C%20also%20runs%20an%20NGO%20that%20rehabilitates%20children%20who%20run%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPookutty%20won%20the%20Oscar%20for%20best%20sound%20mixing%20in%202009%2C%20for%20%3Cem%3ESlumdog%20Millionaire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20has%20worked%20across%20different%20languages%2C%20as%20a%20sound%20director%20for%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3ESaawariya%2C%20Enthiran%2C%20English%20Vinglish%2C%20The%20Best%20Exotic%20Marigold%20Hotel%2C%20Highway%2C%20Pathemari%2C%20Pushpa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20many%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20the%20Kerala%20Literature%20Festival%2C%20Pookutty%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20his%20directorial%20debut%2C%20the%20times%20we%20live%20in%20and%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20Edited%20excerpts%20from%20the%20interview%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20inspired%20you%20to%20move%20to%20directing%3F%20And%20how%20did%20you%20choose%20the%20book%20on%20which%20to%20base%20your%20first%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20filmmaker%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20you%20went%20to%20film%20school.%20Sound%20was%20only%20a%20way%20to%20get%20into%20the%20institute.%20Like%20every%20FTII%20graduate%2C%20I%20also%20nurtured%20the%20ambition%20to%20be%20a%20feature%20filmmaker%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20bad%20one.%20At%20least%20now%20I%20can%20die%20as%20a%20feature%20filmmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20planning%20a%20couple%20of%20films.%20My%20first%20film%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20Hindi%20film%2C%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20For%20various%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20political%20and%20other%20reasons.%20So%20I%20chanced%20upon%20this%20person%2C%20Hariharan%2C%20who%20wrote%20this%20book.%20I%20was%20invited%20for%20a%20function%20where%20they%20reunite%20children%20who%20have%20run%20away%20from%20home%20with%20their%20families.%20They%20rehabilitate%20them.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20this%20function%20and%20I%20saw%20this%20man%20jumping%20around%2C%20doing%20everything.%20He%20was%20introduced%20to%20me%20by%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20friend.%20So%20the%20following%20week%20he%20came%20to%20my%20place%20with%20his%20book%2C%20and%20also%20a%20written%20script.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20way%20the%20book%20was%20interpreted.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20read%20the%20book%20%E2%80%93%20I%20kept%20talking%20to%20him%20about%20his%20life.%20What%20I%20was%20thinking%20was%2C%20see%20a%20film%20is%20not%20a%20book.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20something%20that%20goes%20beyond%20the%20book.%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20about%20his%20life%2C%20what%20it%20is%20that%20makes%20him%20who%20he%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20from%20a%20very%20traditional%20Brahmin%20family%20from%20Palakkad.%20He%20had%20his%20issues%20with%20his%20father%2C%20so%20he%20ran%20away.%20There%20was%20a%20girl%20who%20loved%20him%20very%20dearly.%20But%20he%20thought%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20relate%20to%20her%2C%20she%20was%20from%20a%20very%20traditional%20Brahminical%20family%20and%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20free.%20Three%20times%20he%20ran%20away%20from%20home%3B%20I%20kept%20asking%20him%20why%20he%20ran%20away.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Freedom.%20A%20sense%20of%20freedom.%E2%80%99%20So%20that%20was%20one%20point%20that%20struck%20me.%20And%20this%20girl.%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20when%20you%20came%20back%20and%20became%20what%20you%20became%2C%20did%20you%20ever%20meet%20her%3F%20He%20said%20she%E2%80%99s%20his%20best%20friend%20now.%20But%20he%20never%20got%20married%20to%20her%2C%20though%20she%20was%20in%20love%20with%20him.%20She%20always%20looked%20at%20his%20life%20in%20wonderment%2C%20this%20boy%20who%20ran%20away%20at%20the%20age%20of%208%2C%20then%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20then%20the%20age%20of%2020%E2%80%A6she%20always%20had%20this%20fascination%20about%20him.%20So%20that%20was%20one%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2020%2C%20he%20ran%20away%20and%20went%20to%20Chennai.%20There%20he%20met%20this%20slightly%20older%20man.%20You%20know%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20young%20and%20jubilant%2C%20you%20need%20an%20old%20guy%20in%20your%20life%2C%20a%20friend%2C%20who%20will%20put%20some%20sense%20into%20you.%20Looking%20back%20at%20his%20life%20right%20now%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20this%20man%20paved%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20life.%20In%20whatever%20little%20way%2C%20in%20the%20short%20span%20of%20time%20they%20were%20together.%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20now%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20become%20a%20billionaire%20and%20have%20offices%20all%20across%20India%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%208%2C000%20employees%20%E2%80%93%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20have%20you%20ever%20traced%20this%20man%3F%20Have%20you%20ever%20spoken%20to%20him%3F%20He%20said%2C%20I%20went%20once%20to%20the%20place%20where%20he%20lived%2C%20but%20everything%20had%20changed.%20So%20no.%20I%20never%20found%20him.%20So%20that%20struck%20me%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20the%20film%20can%20be%20a%20letter%20written%20to%20this%20friend%2C%20who%20he%20wants%20to%20find%20now.%20If%20he%20can%20get%20Raju%20%5Bthe%20older%20man%5D%20back%20in%20his%20life%20through%20this%20film%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20very%20happy.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20devising%20the%20film%20as%20a%20letter%20written%20to%20Raju%2C%20and%20an%20unwritten%20letter%20to%20the%20woman%20who%20loved%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20rebellion%20as%20teenagers%20is%20always%20against%20our%20parents.%20Our%20rebellion%20starts%20at%20home.%20And%20we%20as%20parents%20also%20misinterpret%20teenagers%E2%80%99%20sense%20of%20freedom%20as%20rebellion%2C%20and%20we%20get%20worried%20that%20they%20will%20do%20bad%20things%20in%20life.%20So%20the%20film%20is%20a%20complex%20structure%2C%20about%20these%20two%20men%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20But%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20participate%20or%20judge%2C%20the%20film%20just%20watches.%20It%20shows%20life%20as%20it%20is.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20emotional%20rollercoaster%20ride%20for%20Hari%2C%20through%20four%20decades%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20he%20react%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20loved%20it.%20People%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20film%20have%20loved%20it.%20The%20thing%20is%20that%20not%20many%20people%20came%20to%20see%20the%20film%2C%20so%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20love%20that%20part.%20But%20now%20it%20will%20come%20to%20OTT%20platforms%2C%20hopefully%20more%20people%20will%20watch%20it%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20across%20industries%2C%20across%20languages.%20You%20were%20saying%20your%20Hindi%20film%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20made%20because%20of%20political%20reasons.%20Do%20you%20see%20a%20difference%20between%20what%20can%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20said%20in%20different%20industries%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsolutely.%20Everything%20is%20dictated%20by%20the%20time%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20living%20in.%20Artists%20are%20people%20who%20either%20foresee%20this%20time%2C%20or%20bend%20against%20it.%20I%20am%20not%20an%20activist%2C%20so%20I%20am%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20time.%20My%20story%20is%20still%20relevant.%20The%20films%20I%20want%20to%20make%20are%20about%20humanness.%20For%20me%20that%20is%20the%20biggest%20emotion.%20That%20is%20the%20biggest%20language.%20It%20cuts%20across%20all%20languages%2C%20it%20cuts%20across%20all%20the%20sounds%20of%20languages.%20So%20I%20am%20still%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20work%20as%20a%20sound%20designer%2C%20does%20the%20language%20of%20the%20film%20make%20a%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20is%20just%20another%20sound.%20Language%20is%20another%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20another%20directorial%20film%20from%20you%20in%20the%20pipeline%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20planning%20a%20couple%20of%20things.%20I%E2%80%99m%20reading%20scripts%2C%20some%20interesting%20stuff%20has%20come%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20know%20what%20language%20it%20will%20be%20in%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20British%20film%20in%20the%20offering%2C%20two%20Hindi%20films%2C%20a%20Malayalam%20film%20that%20I%20am%20developing.%20I%20really%20want%20to%20work%20in%20my%20language%3B%20I%20have%20a%20command%20over%20it%2C%20I%20write%20in%20it.%20But%20I%20also%20know%20Hindi%20very%20well%2C%20I%20know%20English.%20So%20for%20me%20language%20is%20not%20a%20barrier.%20If%20%5BJafar%5D%20Panahi%20can%20make%20a%20Spanish%20film%2C%20I%20think%20this%20should%20be%20easy%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705490159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17163653%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-17-at-4.35.17-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Feverything-is-dictated-by-the-time-that-were-living-in-resul-pookutty%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oscar-winning%20sound%20designer%20Pookutty%20spoke%20to%20The%20W