-design-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%20will%20receive%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Assam%20Baibhav%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20made%20this%20announcement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20ANI%20said%20Sarma%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20awards%20will%20be%20given%20on%20February%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20year%20on%20which%20the%20awards%20will%20be%20given.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20we%20gave%20the%20Assam%20Baibhav%20award%20to%20Ratan%20Tata%20and%20last%20year%20we%20gave%20the%20award%20to%20Tapan%20Saikia.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20Assam%20government%20has%20selected%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%20for%20the%20Assam%20Baibhav%20award%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1747243331376308526%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20the%20first%20judge%20from%20the%20North%20East%20to%20occupy%20the%20august%20office%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20this%20award%20recognises%20his%20exceptional%20efforts%20to%20expand%20the%20delivery%20of%20justice%20and%20enrich%20our%20jurisprudence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20been%20established%20in%20Ayodhya%20today%20again%2C%20some%20credit%20goes%20to%20an%20Assamese%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20also%20underscored%2C%20according%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fassams-highest-civilian-award-for-ex-cji-ranjan-gogoi%2Farticleshow%2F106921723.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogoi%20became%20a%20nominated%20Rajya%2