0is%20used%20by%20companies%20to%20file%20compliance%20activities%20under%20the%20Companies%20Act%2C%20has%20been%20reported%20to%20have%20many%20software%20glitches%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20The%20latest%20in%20the%20series%20of%20issues%20is%20of%20a%20security%20bug%20where%20Aadhaar-based%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%20details%20of%20every%20company%20director%2C%20including%20industrialists%20and%20celebrities%20like%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20were%20accessible%20without%20authorisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20researcher%20Sai%20Krishna%20Kothapalli%20of%20Hackcrew%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkmskrishna.me%2Fhow-the-personal-data-of-indias-richest-could-have-been-leaked-1952207d9fcd%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealing%20details%20of%20the%20security%20issue.%20The%20report%20disclosed%20how%20the%20issue%20was%20fixed%20only%20after%2011%20months%2C%20after%20it%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-In).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20related%20to%20any%20company%20activity%20is%20made%20available%20to%20the%20general%20public%20for%20carrying%20out%20business%20transactions%20and%20verification%2C%20as%20part%20of%20market%20activities.%20The%20MCA%20portal%20performs%20an%20important%20function%20in%20this%20regard.%20It%20disseminates%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Companies%20Act%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%20KYC%20norms%20exist%20to%20stop%20operations%20of%20shell%20companies%20involved%20in%20any%20illegal%20activities.%20A%20part%20of%20this%20KYC%20information%20is%20shared%20publicly%20to%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20verify%20details%20of%20the%20company%20or%20the%20director%2C%20with%20whom%20they%20are%20entering%20into%20a%20business%20contract%20under%20the%20Companies%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20report%20details%20how%20the%20personal%20information%20that%20was%20available%20to%20be%20accessible%20on%20the%20MCA%20portal%20was%20much%20more%20than%20what%20is%20published%20by%20MCA.%20The%20data%20model%20shared%20in%20the%20report%20shows%20personal%20details%2C%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%20number%2C%20permanent%20account%20number%20(PAN)%2C%20Voter%20ID%2C%20address%2C%20mobile%20number%2C%20and%20email%20ID.%20The%20data%20model%20includes%20internal%20flags%20designated%20by%20MCA%2C%20such%20as%20company%20director%20status%2C%20and%20whether%20director%20address%20is%20shared%20with%20another%20director%20to%20look%20for%20ghost%20directors%20and%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20387px)%2085vw%2C%20387px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17145440%2Fimage-1750.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22387%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17145440%2Fimage-1750.png%20387w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17145440%2Fimage-1750-169x300.png%20169w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693334%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22687%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERedacted%20data%20model%20that%20has%20personal%20details%20of%20Ratan%20Tata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20shows%20yet%20again%20how%20Aadhaar%20data%20that%20is%20being%20collected%20as%20part%20of%20the%20KYC%20process%20is%20often%20leaky%20because%20the%20institutions%20that%20collect%20it%20don%E2%80%99t%20safeguard%20this%20data.%20The%20institutions%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%20quality%20checks%20and%20security%20audits%20are%20Software%20Testing%20and%20Quality%20Certification%20(STQC)%20and%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-In).%20Both%20of%20them%20have%20continued%20to%20fail%20in%20responding%20to%20these%20issues.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Aadhaar%2C%20its%20regulator%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20has%20also%20consistently%20failed%20in%20regulating%20institutions%20that%20have%20leaked%20any%20Aadhaar%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findians-personal-data-breached-yet-again-but-no-sign-that-gaps-will-be-plugged%5C%22%3EIndians%E2%80%99%20Personal%20Data%20Breached%20Yet%20Again%2C%20but%20No%20Sign%20That%20Gaps%20Will%20Be%20Plugged%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20CERT-In%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20all%20security%20vulnerabilities%20disclosed%20to%20them%20and%20immediately%20address%20them.%20Certain%20security%20vulnerabilities%20are%20hard%20to%20fix%20overnight%20and%20do%20require%20time%20to%20issue%20security%20patches%20to%20fix%20them.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20CERT-In%20was%20informed%20about%20the%20security%20issue%20in%20January%202023.%20While%20it%20flagged%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20did%20not%20fix%20it%20immediately.%20Even%20now%2C%20whether%20the%20issue%20is%20completely%20fixed%20is%20unknown%2C%20as%20CERT-In%20does%20not%20conduct%20any%20forensic%20analysis%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20the%20issue%20to%20continue%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20the%20security%20researcher%2011%20months%2C%20from%20January%20to%20December%202023%2C%20to%20analyse%20this%20process.%20The%20analysis%20also%20indicates%20a%20lack%20of%20capacity%20within%20CERT-IN%20to%20address%20such%20issues%2C%20even%20when%20they%20are%20reported%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20security%20bug%20is%20a%20software%20bug%20that%20has%20been%20introduced%20because%20of%20poor%20software%20programming%20and%20quality%20control.%20Company%20secretaries%20and%20chartered%20accountants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fchartered-accountants-flag-concerns-about-glitches-in-mca-21-portal-16462311.htm%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20criticising%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20MCA%20portal%20over%20how%20the%20portal%20has%20several%20software%20issues%20and%20does%20not%20really%20work.%20However%2C%20a%20security%20issue%2C%20couple%20with%20all%20these%20other%20issues%2C%20does%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20The%20lack%20of%20institutional%20accountability%20in%20this%20process%20continues%20to%20show%20how%20no%20one%20inside%20the%20government%20takes%20issues%20related%20to%20software%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20economic%20nature%20of%20this%20information%2C%20several%20companies%20and%20data%20providers%20collect%20this%20information%20and%20are%20already%20providing%20economic%20services%20on%20top%20of%20this%20information.%20There%20is%20an%20entire%20ecosystem%20of%20companies%20that%20provides%20business%20alerts%20and%20changes%20on%20company%20data%20as%20products%20to%20market%20actors%2C%20such%20as%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20investors%2C%20banks%2C%20news%20agencies%2C%20and%20other%20competitors.%20While%20there%20are%20companies%20which%20only%20provide%20information%20that%20is%20publicly%20being%20shared%20by%20the%20MCA%2C%20there%20are%20other%20entities%20which%20share%20the%20personal%20details%20of%20directors%2C%20such%20as%20their%20phone%20numbers%20and%20email%20IDs%2C%20as%20an%20extra%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20organisations%20or%20data%20brokers%20may%20have%20already%20obtained%20part%20or%20full%20information%20of%20these%20companies%20and%20directors%20through%20security%20bugs%20in%20the%20MCA%20portal.%20The%20MCA%20website%20only%20publishes%20basic%20information%20publicly%20when%20any%20user%20wants%20to%20verify%20the%20director%20identification%20number%20or%20their%20PAN.%20This%20is%20not%20excessive%20information%20and%20the%20Companies%20Act%20mandates%20this%20information%20to%20be%20public.%20The%20problem%20is%20with%20the%20additional%20information%2C%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%2C%20PAN%2C%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20and%20email%20ID%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20not%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17150716%2Fmca.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17150716%2Fmca.png%201004w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17150716%2Fmca-300x167.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22559%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERatan%20Tata%E2%80%99s%20director%20identification%20number%20on%20the%20MCA%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20organisations%2C%20such%20as%20government%20departments%2C%20collect%20information%20for%20a%20range%20of%20regulatory%20activities%20and%20are%20often%20legally%20required%20to%20do%20so.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20ministry%20has%20to%20collect%20information%20for%20various%20compliance%20activities%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20is%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20control%20the%20flow%20of%20information%2C%20which%20is%20unacceptable.%20Policies%20like%20the%20National%20Data%20Sharing%20and%20Accessibility%20Policy%20mandate%20government%20departments%20to%20classify%20their%20datasets%20into%20open%2C%20shareable%2C%20and%20restricted%20categories%20to%20ensure%20the%20proper%20management%20of%20data%20flow.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20activity%20has%20largely%20been%20ignored%20by%20government%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdeanonymisation-in-non-personal-data%5C%22%3EWithout%20a%20Data%20Privacy%20Law%2C%20India%20Must%20Consider%20Hazards%20of%20%E2%80%98Deanonymisation%E2%80%99%20of%20Non-Personal%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%202023%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20enforced%2C%20completely%20exempts%20government%20departments.%20Despite%20this%20exemption%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20government%20still%20has%20to%20do%20a%20forensic%20analysis%20to%20identify%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20data%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20has%20announced%20a%20draft%20national%20data%20governance%20policy%2C%20in%20which%20an%20India%20Data%20Management%20Office%20was%20supposed%20to%20classify%20various%20datasets%20with%20the%20government.%20However%2C%20this%20office%20has%20not%20been%20set%20up%20yet%2C%20and%20the%20process%20is%20still%20underway.%20Until%20this%20classification%20takes%20place%2C%20these%20issues%20will%20likely%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20it%20was%20Ratan%20Tata%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-archive%2Fweb%2F2g-tapes-my-privacy-violated-tata-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Eapproached%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demanding%20privacy%20regulation%20after%20his%20telephonic%20conversations%20were%20leaked%20as%20part%20of%20the%202G%20scam%20in%202010.%20Even%20after%20many%20years%2C%20the%20state%20is%20still%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20enforce%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705487034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30142939%2Fcyber-security-1923446_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-bug-in-mca-portal-leaked-aadhaar-based-kyc-details-of-indias-top-industrialists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Security%20researcher%20Sai%20Krishna%20Kothapalli%20of%20Hackcrew%20published%20a%20report%20revealing%20details%20of%20the%20security%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-bug-in-mca-portal-leaked-aadhaar-based-kyc-details-of-indias-top-industrialists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reading%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20Against%20Practices%20in%20Delhi%20University%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F14161808%2FDelhi-university.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20back%20to%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%202020%20and%20read%20it%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20I%3F%20That%2C%20we%20the%20teachers%20and%20students%20in%20higher%20education%20are%20told%2C%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20all%20that%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%3B%20one%20short%20hand%20that%20justifies%20the%20new%20steps%3B%20one%3Cem%3E%20open%20sesame%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20newness%2C%20if%20you%20like!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20educational%20policy%20of%20the%2021st%20century%E2%80%9D%2C%20intended%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Coperational%20during%202030-2040%E2%80%9D%2C%20presents%20certain%20aspects%20as%20foundational%20and%20it%20would%20be%20good%20to%20review%20these%20ideas%20against%20the%20steps%20taken%20so%20far%20using%20the%20teaching%20experience%20in%20Delhi%20University%20%E2%80%93%20an%20early%20bird%20and%20thus%20a%20likely%20forerunner%20in%20NEP%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHolistic%20development%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20mantra%20in%20the%20NEP.%20The%20NEP%20argues%20against%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20hard%20separation%E2%80%9D%20of%20arts%20and%20sciences%20as%20well%20as%20between%20curricular%20and%20extra-curricular%20activities.%20Student-run%2C%20faculty-mentored%20clubs%20and%20activities%20are%20said%20to%20be%20so%20important%20that%20the%20NEP%20has%20provisions%20for%20funding%20them!%20But%20in%20Delhi%20University%2C%20where%20I%20teach%2C%20the%20NEP%20system%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20courses%20for%20students%2C%20leaving%20them%20in%20the%20class%20room%20practically%20throughout%20the%20day.%20The%20number%20of%20classes%20in%20courses%20has%20been%20reduced%20%E2%80%93%20when%20many%20of%20these%20courses%20were%20taught%20with%20almost%20the%20same%20content%20and%20in%2060%25%20of%20the%20number%20of%20lectures%20in%20the%20earlier%20scheme.%20This%20overcrowded%20scheme%20not%20only%20makes%20learning%20rushed%2C%20summary-based%20and%20superfluous%20but%20also%20takes%20away%20the%20time%20for%20student%20activities%2C%20diminishing%20their%20%E2%80%9Cholistic%20development%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEP%20does%20talk%20about%20its%20aim%20to%20make%20the%20student%20number%20in%20higher%20education%20institutions%203%2C000%2C%20with%20a%20promise%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20student-teacher%20ratio%20will%20not%20be%20too%20high%E2%80%9D%20and%20insisting%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cphysical%20infrastructure%20and%20appropriate%20resources%20conducive%20for%20learning%E2%80%9D.%20If%20student%20numbers%20are%20increased%20(as%20Delhi%20University%20colleges%20have%20increased%20seats%20up%20to%2020%25)%20without%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20teachers%20and%20building%20infrastructure%20and%20resources%2C%20it%20goes%20against%20the%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CQuality%20classroom%20transaction%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20passing%20mention%20in%20the%20document%2C%20there%20lay%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMultidisciplinarity%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20central%20and%20most%20repeated%20NEP%20theme.%20In%20its%20conceptualisation%20of%20a%20Four%20Year%20Undergraduate%20Programme%2C%20a%20student%20has%20multiple%20exit%20options%20the%20NEP%20offers%3A%20after%20one%20year%2C%20certificate%3B%20after%20two%20years%2C%20diploma%3B%20after%20three%20years%2C%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%3B%20and%20after%20four%2C%20multidisciplinary%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20The%20first%20year%20is%20over%20and%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20how%20many%20left%20with%20a%20certificate.%20Whatever%20that%20number%20is%2C%20the%20difficulty%20is%20that%20the%20first%20year%20courses%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20formulated%20with%20such%20cohesiveness%20that%20there%20looks%20a%20beginning%2C%20middle%20and%20end%20for%20it%20as%20a%20one%20year%20stand-alone%20entity.%20Under%20the%20category%20of%20Value%20Added%20Courses%20and%20Skill%20Enhancement%20Courses%2C%20a%20number%20of%20courses%20have%20been%20introduced%3A%20any%20department%20can%20teach%20these%20courses%20without%20worrying%20about%20expertise%20and%20specialisation%2C%20caricaturing%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmultidisciplinarity%E2%80%9D!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTeacher%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NEP%20proclaims%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20all%20reforms%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20learning%20process%E2%80%9D%20and%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20mentors%20as%20well.%20While%20the%20NEP%20talks%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctenure%20track%E2%80%9D%20(a%20sort%20of%20probation)%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctenure%E2%80%9D%20(permanent)%20in%20proper%20American%20university%20terms%2C%20this%20is%20the%20domain%20in%20which%20the%20cruellest%20kind%20of%20exploitation%20has%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20ad%20hoc%20appointment%20system%20had%20three%20benefits%3A%20ad%20hoc%20teachers%20were%20paid%20almost%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20that%20of%20an%20entry%20level%20permanent%20staff%20minus%20increments%20and%20some%20allowances%2C%20their%20experience%20counted%20when%20they%20applied%20for%20permanent%20jobs%2C%20for%20their%20promotions%20later%2C%20and%20they%20had%20vacation%20salary%20if%20they%20worked%20on%20the%20last%20and%20first%20day%20of%20the%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20the%20new%20guest%20system%20%E2%80%93%20where%20each%20guest%20can%20only%20handle%20half%20the%20workload%20of%20an%20ad%20hoc%2C%20they%20are%20paid%20by%20the%20teaching%20hour%20which%20effectively%20means%20paid%20only%20for%208%20out%20of%2012%20months%20with%20no%20vacation%20salary%20and%20their%20guest%20teaching%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20count%20as%20teaching%20experience.%20Over-worked%2C%20under-paid%20and%20undocumented%20labour%20of%20young%20minds%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20teacher%20centricism!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20horrible%20backlog%20of%20permanent%20appointments%20in%20Delhi%20University%20created%20another%20issue%3A%20many%20long-serving%20ad%20hocs%2C%20some%20more%20than%20of%20a%20decade%2C%20got%20displaced%20from%20their%20job%2C%20and%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20departments%20went%20thanklessly%20unaccounted%20for.%20Due%20to%20the%20fast%20forwarded%20nature%20of%20interviews%2C%20some%20actually%20lasted%20only%20for%20a%20minute%20or%20two%2C%20and%20serious%20allegations%20of%20favouritism%20in%20some%20colleges%20students%20got%20pushed%20into%20staging%20protests%20against%20this%20unfair%20treatment%20of%20teachers%2C%20making%20one%20wonder%20whatever%20happened%20to%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cteacher%20centrality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assessment%20systems%2C%20the%20suggested%20criterion-based%20grading%20system%20with%20more%20continuous%20and%20comprehensive%20evaluation%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmoving%20away%20from%20high%20stake%20examinations%E2%80%9D%20has%20increased%20the%20internal%20mark%20component.%20Given%20the%20number%20of%20courses%20a%20student%20has%20to%20attend%2C%20the%20number%20of%20graded%20tasks%20in%20a%20semester%20and%20the%20persistent%20bureaucratic%20notions%2C%20teachers%20would%20be%20tripling%20up%20as%20exam%20superintends%2C%20invigilators%20and%20evaluators%2C%20all%20rolled%20into%20one%2C%20for%20most%20of%20the%20teaching%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20NEP%20is%20in%20such%20contrast%20with%20the%20stated%20projects%2C%20who%20is%20to%20be%20blamed%3F%20I%20think%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20professors%20sitting%20in%20on%20the%20highest%20decision-making%20bodies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20academic%20council%20and%20the%20executive%20council%2C%20for%20they%20do%20not%20use%20their%20discerning%20power%2C%20domain%20expertise%20and%20educational%20experience%20ethically%20in%20heralding%20a%20newly%20developed%20policy%20to%20an%20area%20they%20are%20in%20charge%20of.%20Either%20there%20is%20cynical%20resignation%20or%20timid%20collaboration%20with%20some%20policy%20makers%20%E2%80%93%20in%20both%20cases%20they%20are%20not%20doing%20their%20job.%20This%20chasm%20between%20what%20is%20said%20and%20what%20is%20done%20will%20waste%20our%20public%20universities%20into%20a%20demonetised%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inefficiency%20and%20the%20mayhem%20witnessed%20in%20admissions%2C%20course%20content%2C%20academic%20directives%20and%20examination%20process%20in%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20year%20have%20started%20demonstrating%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEP%20concludes%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20need%20to%20have%20comprehensiveness%20in%20implementation%20and%20the%20need%20to%20review%20the%20linkages%20between%20multiple%20parallel%20steps%20and%20in%20such%20a%20task%20is%20undertaken%20with%20its%20implemented%20version%2C%20the%20NEP%20is%20unlikely%20to%20recognise%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organising%20principles%20of%20the%20NEP%20were%20always%20contested.%20There%20is%20an%20Indian%20story%20in%20education%20which%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20India%20being%20the%20largest%20provider%20of%20skilled%20engineers%20for%20the%20knowledge%20economy%20and%20its%20substantial%20contribution%20to%20the%20global%20academic%20scene.%20This%20immediate%20past%20was%20totally%20hidden%20and%20an%20ancient%20India%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20age%20narrative%E2%80%9D%20was%20formulated%20to%20redress%20the%20majoritarian%20fears%2C%20concocted%20by%20the%20majoritarian%20political%20propaganda%20of%20fear%20and%20inferiority.%20This%20obsession%20is%20one%20major%20flaw%20of%20the%20NEP.%20Moreover%2C%20its%20deployment%20of%20choice%20and%20freedom%20seem%20to%20address%20consumers%20of%20an%20academic%20mall%20and%20not%20citizens-in-the-making%20of%20a%20republic%20(This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20earlier%20it%20was%20all%20picture%20perfect.%20In%20experience%2C%20the%20shift%20might%20just%20be%20from%20one%20that%20scared%20students%20as%20subjects%20to%20one%20that%20is%20scared%20of%20students%20as%20consumers).%20The%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20secret%20agenda%2C%20those%20who%20disagreed%20maintained%2C%20is%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20social%20sector%20by%20emptying%20out%20the%20existing%20organisations%20of%20character%20and%20quality%20and%20enabling%20the%20market%20players%20to%20extract%20wealth%20from%20the%20moneyed%20for%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20those%20views%20are%20kept%20out%20for%20now%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20NEP%20supporters%20be%20specially%20concerned%2C%20if%20their%20journey%20to%20the%20promised%20land%20of%20Indian%20education%20has%20already%20started%20on%20missteps%2C%20with%20so%20much%20being%20out%20of%20syllabus%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20new%20world%20order%20in%20the%20making%2C%20techno-economic%20givens%2C%20insights%20in%20educational%20philosophy%20and%20psychology%2C%20generational%20conflicts%20and%20paradigm%20shifts%20accelerated%20by%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20environmental%20scene%2C%20nobody%20will%20say%20our%20educational%20practices%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20revision.%20Indian%20educational%20system%E2%80%99s%20reach%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20its%20socialist%20proclamations%20till%201990s%20or%20a%20mixed%20situation%20thereafter%2C%20went%20beyond%20feudal%2C%20upper%20caste%2C%20metropolitan%20and%20plutocratic%20constraints%20only%20in%20exceptions%20and%20that%20does%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20corrected.%20But%20all%20these%20require%20an%20inclusive%20and%20egalitarian%20vision%20for%20the%20future%2C%20a%20plan%20that%20can%20actualise%20it%20and%20an%20institutional%20system%20that%20can%20perform%20this%20script%20with%20understanding%20and%20rigour%20%E2%80%93%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20existing%20institutional%20structures%20for%20the%20spectacle%20of%20old%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20the%20new%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20begin%20to%20do%20it.%20What%20falls%20through%20the%20cracks%20of%20NEP%20theory%20and%20practice%20is%20the%20future%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20like%20that%20of%20Trishanku%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Ikshwaku%20king%20sent%20to%20heaven%20alive%20with%20the%20blessing%20of%20a%20powerful%20human-sage%20but%20was%20stopped%20without%20getting%20entry%20by%20the%20enraged%20chief%20of%20gods.%20The%20king%20hanging%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20struggling%20in%20the%20neither-here-nor-here%20of%20empty%20air%20is%20a%20suitable%20but%20sad%20metaphor%20for%20what%20Indian%20higher%20education%20scene%20is%20living%20through%3A%20one%20that%20we%20need%20to%20take%20urgent%20notice%20of%20but%2C%20as%20a%20people%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20get%20accustomed%20to!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.P.%20Ashley%20teaches%20English%20at%20St.%20Stephen%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705486637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F14161808%2FDelhi-university.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Freading-the-national-education-policy-against-practices-in-delhi-university%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20implementation%20of%20the%20NEP%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20its%20stated%20projects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Freading-the-national-education-policy-against-practices-in-delhi-university%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flight%20Delays%3A%20Maintenance%20Setback%20at%20Delhi%20Airport%20Runway%20Over%20'G20%2C%20Pollution%20Curbs'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17133238%2FSculpture_of_hasta_mudras_at_Indira_Gandhi_International_Airport.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Delhi%20International%20Airport%20Limited%20(DIAL)%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20with%20reasons%20behind%20the%20delay%20in%20re-carpeting%20the%20second%20runway%20at%20the%20facility%C2%A0after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20ministry%20pulled%20up%20DIAL%20over%20the%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20fog-related%20delays%20that%20hit%20flight%20operations%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Indian%20Express%2C%20DIAL%20explained%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20compressed%20timeline%20post-G20%20Summit%20in%20September%20and%20pollution-related%20curbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20imposed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20posed%20challenges%20to%20completing%20the%20project%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20GRAP%20IV%20norms%2C%20due%20to%20pollution%20concerns%2C%20disrupted%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20civil%20works%2C%20the%20airport%20operator%20said.%20GRAP%20IV%20restrictions%2C%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20November%205%20last%20year%2C%20banned%20the%20entry%20of%20polluting%20vehicles%20from%20other%20states%20in%20Delhi%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20curbs%20to%20combat%20the%20poor%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDIAL%20also%20highlighted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Edelays%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20runway%20lights%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20supply%20chain%20complexities%20and%20unexpected%20challenges%20during%20the%20cable-laying%20process%2C%20including%20duct%20blockages.%20Despite%20these%20challenges%2C%20DIAL%20has%20assured%20the%20ministry%20that%20it%20will%20meet%20the%20January%2019%20deadline%20for%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20re-carpeting%20work%20pertains%20to%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%E2%80%99s%20(IGIA)%20second%20runway%2C%20known%20as%2028%2F10.%20Once%20completed%2C%20the%20airport%20authority%20will%20initiate%20steps%20to%20make%20the%20runway%20CAT%20III%20compliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT%20III%20compliance%20allows%20for%20landing%20in%20very%20low%20visibility%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20fog%2C%20rain%2C%20or%20snow.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20has%20one%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20runway%2C%2029L%2F11R%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccity%20side%E2%80%9D%20or%20Gurgaon.%20The%20newest%20runway%2C%2011L%2F29R%2C%20is%20only%20partially%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20and%20is%20awaiting%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20re-carpeting%20is%20finished%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20will%20conduct%20an%20inspection%20to%20identify%20any%20necessary%20changes.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20DGCA%20inspection%20has%20already%20been%20carried%20out%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20flights%20have%20been%20disrupted%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20because%20of%20fog%20in%20north%20India.%20In%20new%20rules%20to%20tackle%20the%20airport%20chaos%2C%20the%20aviation%20ministry%20has%20asked%20airlines%20to%20cancel%20flights%20delayed%20beyond%20three%20hours%2C%20NDTV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fco-passenger-on-indigo-flight-shares-what-happened-before-man-slapped-pilot-4872271%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705484671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17133238%2FSculpture_of_hasta_mudras_at_Indira_Gandhi_International_Airport.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fflight-delays-maintenance-setback-at-delhi-airport-runway-over-g20-pollution-curbs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20compressed%20timeline%20post-G20%20Summit%20in%20September%20and%20pollution-related%20curbs%20imposed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20posed%20challenges%20to%20completing%20the%20project%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time%2C%20the%20airport%20operator%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fflight-delays-maintenance-setback-at-delhi-airport-runway-over-g20-pollution-curbs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Full%20Text%20%7C%20'Only%20Political%20Hindus%20Are%20Happy'%3A%20Shankaracharya%20on%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15174928%2FEffect-67.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmid%20the%20buzz%20around%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Karan%20Thapar%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20interviewed%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%2C%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati.%20All%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20noted%20their%20objection%20to%20the%20consecration%2C%20underscoring%20that%20Hindu%20Shastras%20do%20not%20permit%20performing%20the%20consecration%20of%20a%20deity%20in%20an%20incomplete%20temple.%20They%20also%20noted%20that%20January%2022%20falls%20in%20the%20lunar%20month%20of%20Paus%2C%20which%20is%20inauspicious%20for%20the%20ceremony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHis%20disappointment%20is%20palpable%20in%20the%20interview%20and%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20says%20only%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20consecration%2C%20not%20the%20scores%20of%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20Hindus%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%2040-minute%20interview%2C%20he%20covers%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%2C%20highlighting%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20politicisation%20of%20a%20religious%20event.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20full%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style%2C%20clarity%2C%20and%20syntax.%20Sentences%20in%20Hindi%20have%20been%20translated.%20The%20translation%20and%20transcription%20has%20been%20done%20by%20Sagarika%20Chaudhary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20With%20exactly%20a%20week%20left%20for%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20special%20guest%20today.%20He%20is%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%2C%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati.%20Swami%20%3Cem%3EJi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20thank%20you%20very%20much%20for%20agreeing%20to%20give%20me%20this%20interview.%20I%20hope%20you%20will%20forgive%20me%20if%20I%20ask%20you%20questions%20in%20English%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20language%20I%20speak%20much%20better.%20Let%20me%20start%20with%20the%20obvious%20question.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20have%20you%20refused%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20the%2022nd%20of%20January%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20I%20have%20not%20refused%20any%20invitation.%20The%20truth%20is%2C%20that%20we%20have%20not%20been%20invited%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20not%20received%20the%20invitation%20up%20till%20now%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes.%20That%20is%20why%20no%20one%20can%20accuse%20us%20of%20refusing%20any%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20be%20the%20reason%20behind%20them%20not%20having%20sent%20an%20invitation%20to%20you%20till%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20question%20that%20should%20be%20posed%20to%20those%20distributing%20the%20invitations%2C%20about%20why%20they%20have%20not%20sent%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20they%20not%20sent%20an%20invitation%20to%20only%20you%20or%20have%20the%20other%20three%20Shankracharyas%20not%20received%20one%2C%20either%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20about%20them%2C%20but%20I%20can%20about%20myself%2C%2