%C2%A0He%20also%20says%20that%20those%20who%20disobey%20these%20commandments%20and%20do%20what%20they%20want%20instead%2C%20cannot%20gain%20enlightenment%20and%20success.%C2%A0%5BSanskrit%20shloka%5D%20This%20means%20that%20our%20scriptures%20and%20God%20have%20commanded%20that%20one%20should%20work%20according%20to%20the%20commandments%20and%20not%20do%20anything%20opposing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwami%20Ji%2C%20one%20of%20your%20videos%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20wherein%20you%20say%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20anti-Modi%2C%20but%20I%20cannot%20be%20anti-Dharmashastra%20either.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20this%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20trying%20to%20explain%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20is%20this%20very%20thing%20that%20I%20have%20been%20explaining%2C%20and%20I%20used%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98anti-Modi%E2%80%99%20there%20because%20that%20was%20the%20context.%20It%20is%20mandatory%20for%20me%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20scriptures%20and%20I%20would%20want%20religious%20proceedings%20to%20take%20place%20in%20the%20right%20way%20when%20I%20am%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20only%20if%20it%20is%20a%20religious%20proceeding.%20However%2C%20if%20not%2C%20then%20it%20is%20not%20my%20jurisdiction%20and%20then%2C%20I%20will%20not%20say%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUp%20till%20now%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20being%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20yet%20complete.%20Even%20the%20shikhar%20of%20the%20temple%20has%20not%20been%20built.%20Do%20the%20scriptures%20say%20that%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20of%20a%20temple%20cannot%20happen%20if%20the%20temple%20is%20incomplete%20and%20unfinished%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20our%20scriptures%20have%20clearly%20said%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20the%20body%20of%20God%20and%20the%20idol%20is%20the%20soul.%20So%20the%20temple%20is%20the%20body%20and%20the%20kalash%20is%20the%20head.%20So%20right%20now%2C%20the%20shikhar%20is%20not%20yet%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20our%20body%20is%20built%20from%20head%20to%20toe%2C%20God%E2%80%99s%20body%20is%20symbolised%20by%20the%20temple.%20In%20the%20body%2C%20the%20head%2C%20the%20eyes%2C%20the%20mouth%20remain%20incomplete%20because%20the%20shikhar%20is%20not%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20such%20a%20state%2C%20when%20the%20head%20has%20not%20been%20built%2C%20how%20can%20you%20place%20the%20soul%20inside%20the%20body%3F%20This%20would%20be%20a%20dire%20mistake%2C%20not%20one%20that%20has%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20newspapers%2C%20I%20have%20read%20that%20the%20garb%20griha%20is%20ready.%20When%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20can%20we%20have%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20garb%20griha%20essentially%20means%20almost%20like%20the%20womb%20of%20the%20mother%20is%20ready.%20Even%20if%20there%20is%20life%20in%20the%20womb%2C%20it%20is%20not%20revealed%20to%20us.%20It%20will%20take%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20his%20hands%20and%20legs%20will%20be%20formed%2C%20Then%20he%20will%20gain%20sense%2C%20and%20only%20after%20nine%20months%20when%20his%20body%20is%20fully%20formed%20will%20he%20come%20out%20so%20that%20people%20can%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20garb%20griha%20is%20ready%2C%20so%20the%20baby%20has%20been%20conceived%2C%20but%20the%20body%20has%20not%20been%20formed.%20Till%20the%20body%20is%20formed%2C%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20cannot%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20read%20another%20thing%20which%20states%20that%20the%2022nd%20of%20January%20is%20an%20auspicious%20occasion%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple.%20Do%20you%20agree%20with%20this%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20is%20auspicious%2C%20then%20there%20are%20about%20100%20crore%20Hindus%20or%20Sanatanis%20in%20India%20and%20they%20all%20have%20a%20calendar%20to%20determine%20auspiciousness%20because%2080%25%20of%20people%20believe%20in%20the%20importance%20of%20choosing%20an%20auspicious%20day%20for%20most%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20we%20buy%20a%20Hindu%20calendar%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20is%20used%20more%20now.%20Even%20then%2C%20people%20believe%20in%20auspicious%20days%2C%20festivals%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20buy%20the%20Hindu%20calendar%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20calendar%20has%20all%20auspicious%20days%20in%20it%20which%20say%20what%20activity%20should%20be%20done%20when%2C%20including%20temple%20building%2C%20weddings%2C%20etc.%20I%20want%20to%20see%20one%20calendar%20in%20India%20which%20has%20printed%2022nd%20January%20as%20the%20right%20day%20to%20do%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20all%20the%20priests%20who%20bear%20the%20responsibility%20of%20making%20the%20calendar%20not%20been%20able%20to%20see%20the%20auspiciousness%20of%20this%20date%2C%20and%20only%20one%20person%20has%20been%20able%20to%3F%20Why%20has%20no%20one%20else%20been%20able%20to%20see%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20date%20was%20so%20auspicious%20that%20the%20Lord%20Ram%20who%20took%20500%20years%20to%20build%20could%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20temple%2C%20why%20did%20the%20priests%20not%20catch%20on%20and%20print%20about%20this%20day%20in%20the%20calendar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20checked%20on%2010-15%20calendars%20personally%20and%20consulted%20with%20multiple%20people%20who%20say%20that%20it%20is%20not%20mentioned%20that%20this%20day%20is%20very%20auspicious%20for%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20priest%20who%20has%20deemed%20this%20auspicious%20is%20from%20Kashi%2C%20and%20he%20is%20wise.%20We%20all%20respect%20him.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20interviews%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20deem%20an%20auspicious%20day%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20was%20asked%20to%20do%20so%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20he%20has%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20in%20a%20way%2C%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20name%20a%20day%20in%20January%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20he%20said%20that%20I%20was%20told%20to%20name%20a%20day%20in%20January%2C%20so%20I%20named%20this%20one%2C%20whichever%20day%20seemed%20right%20in%20January.%20This%20means%20that%20someone%20had%20prompted%20him%20to%20name%20a%20day%20in%20this%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20it%2C%20whatever%20seemed%20right%20is%20what%20he%20told%20them.%20So%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20priest%20is%20at%20fault%20because%20he%20was%20given%20a%20time%20frame%2C%20and%20in%20it%2C%20he%20named%20the%20day%20he%20thought%20was%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20I%20listen%20to%20you%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20you%20are%20reluctant%20to%20go.%20Even%20if%20you%20had%20been%20invited%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20you%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20present.%20Is%20it%20also%20true%E2%80%93%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20if%20I%20received%20an%20invitation%2C%20I%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20Ayodhya%20but%20not%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20temple%20activities%2C%20so%20the%20invitation%20could%20be%20respected%C2%A0because%20if%20you%20receive%20an%20invitation%20from%20God%2Cso%20our%20learning%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20say%20we%20should%20refuse%20it%2C%20so%20we%20would%20have%20gone%20till%20there%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETill%20Ayodhya%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20Ayodhya%20to%20say%20that%20we%20have%20accepted%20your%20invitation%20but%20we%20cannot%20be%20part%20of%20the%20proceedings%20because%20we%20cannot%20see%20something%20unlawful%20happen%20in%20front%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20reported%20in%20the%20papers%20that%20the%20Shankracharyas%20of%20Puri%2C%20Dwarka%20and%20Shangeri%20are%20also%20not%20going%2C%20can%20you%20confirm%20that%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20neither%20of%20us%20are%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20four%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20are%20not%20going%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20knowledge%20up%20till%20now%2C%20no%20one.%20Who%20can%20say%20what%20might%20happen%20in%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Only%20seven%20days%20are%20left%2C%20Shankaracharya%20ji%2C%20in%20seven%20days%20people%E2%80%99s%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%20won%E2%80%99t%20change.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20can%20change%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20seconds%2C%20but%20according%20to%20the%20situation%20now%2C%20no%20one%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Based%20on%20the%20situation%20right%20now%2C%20all%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20are%20not%20going%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20they%20are%20not%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20when%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20happens%2C%20the%20central%20person%20at%20it%20will%20be%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20has%20said%20the%20following%20about%20this%2C%20I%20will%20read%20it%20for%20you%3A%20Our%20scriptures%20have%20clearly%20mentioned%20who%20can%20touch%20the%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20I%20do%20there%20during%20the%20consecration%3F%20The%20PM%20will%20touch%20the%20idol.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20stand%20there%20and%20clap%20to%20applaud%20him.%20I%20know%20the%20dignity%20of%20my%20position%2C%20this%20is%20not%20ego.%20Do%20you%20share%20those%20views%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20absolutely.%20He%20is%20right.%20Their%20words%20can%20be%20different%2C%20but%20what%20they%20mean%20is%20that%20the%20rules%20are%20not%20being%20followed%20which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20not%20right%20for%20us%20to%20be%20there.%20He%20is%20also%20calling%20it%20unlawful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20stop%20it%20because%20there%20will%20be%20external%20pressures%20there%20and%20in%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20not%20go%2C%20which%20is%20what%20he%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20all%20four%20of%20you%20hold%20this%20position%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20natural.%20All%20our%20scriptures%20are%20the%20same%2C%20we%20are%20different%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20area%2C%20our%20rules%20are%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020-300x184.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020-1024x627.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692406%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22735%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20performing%20bhoomi%20pujan%20at%20Ram%20Mandir.%20Also%20visible%20are%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20and%20Anandiben%20Patel.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20an%20impression%20in%20the%20country%20that%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20has%20become%20political%20rather%20than%20religious.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20discussion%20around%20the%20temple%20is%20political%2C%20it%20has%20ceased%20to%20be%20religious.%20If%20it%20was%20about%20religion%2C%20we%20would%20have%20been%20consulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20a%20trust%20of%20the%20Dharmacharyas%20called%20the%20Ramalyaya%20Trust%20had%20already%20existed.%20In%201997%20when%20the%20land%20around%20the%20temple%20came%20to%20be%20contested%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20there%20would%20be%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20proceedings%2C%20whoever%20wins%2C%20be%20it%20the%20Hindus%20or%20the%20Muslims%2C%20will%20be%20given%20the%20land%20for%20establishing%20their%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20Trust%20was%20discarded%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20place%20of%20which%20the%20Ramalyay%20Trust%20was%20established%20in%20case%20the%20Hindus%20won%20the%20land.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20established%20a%20Trust%20of%20his%20own%20workers%C2%A0which%20he%20announced%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20It%20was%20clear%20that%20a%20temple%20was%20to%20be%20built%20which%20means%20that%20the%20primary%20role%20is%20of%20the%20Dharmacharyas%20since%20they%20are%20men%20of%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20they%20should%20be%20held%20responsible%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20religious%20act.%20But%20instead%20of%20doing%20that%20which%20would%20have%20been%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20here%2C%20then%20Narasimha%20Rao%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20said%20that%20we%20should%20make%20the%20trust%20after%20the%20Court%20ordered.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20one%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20could%E2%80%99ve%20made%20his%20own%20Trust%20if%20he%20wanted%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20Modi%20did.%20All%20the%20important%20priests%20were%20included%20in%20the%20Trust%2C%20but%20he%20removed%20that%20and%20put%20Party%20workers%20in%20place%20of%20them.%20It%20became%20clear%20at%20that%20moment%20that%20religion%20will%20be%20overlooked%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20overlooking%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%20then%2C%20because%20no%20one%20was%20consulted%20and%20their%20suggestions%20were%20not%20asked%20for%20in%20the%20building%20of%20the%20temple.%20They%20have%20never%20spoken%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20priests%20have%20never%20been%20consulted%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20not%20just%20that%2C%20even%20in%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20they%20did%20not%20consult%20us%2C%20and%20did%20everything%2C%20telling%20everyone%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20everything%20right.This%20is%20the%20important%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20talking%2C%20Shankaracharya%20ji%2C%20about%20how%20politics%20and%20politicians%20have%20interfered%20in%20the%20building%20of%20the%20temple.%20The%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20has%20said%20in%20Bengal%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20came%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20and%20I%20will%20read%20out%20to%20you%3A%20Politicians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20they%20have%20responsibilities%20under%20the%20constitution.%20There%20are%20rules%20and%20restrictions%20in%20the%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20domain%2C%20and%20these%20rules%20should%20be%20followed.%20Interference%20in%20every%20area%20by%20politicians%20is%20insanity.%20Overstepping%20these%20rules%20for%20propagating%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20an%20act%20of%20rebellion%20against%20God.%20Do%20you%20agree%20with%20this%20thought%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20fully%20agree.%20I%20agree%20100%25%20because%20our%20thoughts%20have%20been%20expressed%20perfectly%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20at%20Puri.%C2%A0I%20would%20like%20to%20add%20further%20to%20clarify%20that%20everyone%20has%20a%20limit%2C%20not%20just%20politicians.%20If%20I%20start%20interfering%20in%20politics%2C%20I%20will%20also%20be%20crossing%20my%20limit%2C%20and%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20politicians%20should%20not%20interfere%20in%20religion.%20Both%20should%20understand%20their%20limits%20and%20remain%20in%20them%20apart%20from%20occasionally%20helping%20each%20other.%20This%20is%20a%20religion%20where%20Dharmacharyas%20will%20be%20important%20and%20no%20other%20man%20can%20be%20more%20important%2C%20this%20is%20clear.%C2%A0This%20is%20something%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20clear%20right%20now%20at%20the%20holy%20land%20of%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20because%20it%20can%20potentially%20become%20harmful%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20people%20will%20start%20insulting%20the%20scriptures%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20But%20the%20words%20used%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20are%20very%20powerful.%20He%20says%20politicians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20interfering%20in%20every%20area%20by%20politicians%20is%20insanity.%20And%20then%20he%20says%20overstepping%20these%20rules%20for%20propagating%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20an%20act%20of%20rebellion%20against%20God.%20I%20think%20that%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20is%20referring%20to%20Mr.%20Modi.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20hidden%20statement%2C%20everyone%20can%20understand%20what%20it%20means.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20one%20can%20only%20see%20Mr.%20Modi%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20you%2C%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20everyone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20hidden%20fact%20that%20one%20man%20is%20running%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%20tell%20me%20this%2C%20Shankaracharya%20Ji%2C%20are%20you%20worried%20that%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20been%20politicised%20and%20that%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20propaganda%20surrounding%20it%3F%20And%20this%20could%20end%20up%20dividing%20India%20rather%20than%20uniting%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20that%20is%20the%20worry.%20The%20concern%20is%20that%20they%20are%20being%20divisive.%20They%20are%20dividing%20the%20religious%20Hindus%20and%20the%20politicised%20Hindus%2C%20and%20the%20representative%20you%20have%20chosen%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20consult%20the%20priests%20who%20understand%20the%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sort%20of%20divisive%20sentiment%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20person%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20not%20just%20uniting%20the%20Hindus%20of%20India%2C%20but%20India%20as%20a%20whole%20by%20some%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20had%20said%20that%20this%20is%20a%20national%20temple%20which%20is%20being%20constructed.%20Is%20this%20how%20you%20will%20make%20a%20national%20temple%3F%20You%20should%20have%20united%20all%20Indians%20regardless%20of%20religion%2C%20but%20you%20have%20managed%20to%20divide%20the%20Hindus%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20Hinduism%2C%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20the%20Maryada%20Purushottam%2C%20or%20the%20ideal%2C%20most%20righteous%20man%2C%20how%20would%20he%20view%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20his%20name%20in%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20matter.%20Bringing%20Ram%20is%20not%20bringing%20his%20idol%2C%20it%20means%20bringing%20his%20righteousness%2C%20his%20ideals%2C%20his%20justice%2C%20his%20sacrifice%2C%20his%20love%20for%20his%20home%20and%20his%20people%2C%20that%20is%20when%20he%20will%20arrive.%20Lanka%20was%20made%20of%20gold%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20visit%20despite%20Vibhashan%20begging%20him%20after%20his%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Lanka%20might%20be%20of%20gold%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20it%20because%20my%20birthplace%20Ayodhya%20is%20what%20I%20love%20the%20most%20and%20where%20I%20want%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20riches%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20that%20home.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20learn%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20teachings%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20bringing%20Ram%20to%20Ayodhya%3F%20We%20want%20people%20to%20learn%20his%20teachings%2C%20that%20kingdom%20is%20nothing%20compared%20to%20your%20word%2C%20or%20goodness.%C2%A0If%20these%20teachings%20are%20not%20being%20transferred%2C%20then%20our%20temples%20are%20a%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20understand.%20Tell%20me%20this%2C%20Shankaracharya%20jI%2C%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20is%20being%20built.%20Do%20you%20think%20there%20should%20be%20similar%20temples%20made%20in%20place%20of%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20am%20in%20favour%20of%20that.%20I%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20living%20in%20one%20nation%20and%20any%20points%20of%20tension%20should%20be%20solved%20immediately.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20in%20some%20places%2C%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20there%20is%20contestation%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20solve%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20there%20is%20no%20animosity%20between%20two%20religions%20and%20in%20that%2C%20religious%20places%20can%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20that%20harmony%20by%20returning%20them%20to%20who%20they%20originally%20belonged%20to%2C%20In%20the%201950s%20manifesto%20by%20Dharam%20Samrat%20for%20Ram%20Rajya%20Parishad%20wrote%20that%20if%20they%20get%20elected%2C%20they%20will%20ensure%20that%20all%20places%20captured%20by%20Hndus%20which%20belonged%20to%20the%20Muslims%20and%20vice%20versa%20would%20be%20given%20back%20to%20their%20original%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20I%20understand%20you%20correctly%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20that%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20place%20of%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20is%20essential%20and%20important%2C%20it%20must%20happen%2C%20but%20should%20we%20keep%20going%20further%20and%20further%3F%20Do%20we%20want%20to%20identify%20mosques%20built%20on%20temples%20and%20demolish%20them%20or%20is%20it%20a%20full%20stop%20after%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20only%20know%20this%20through%20discussion%20which%20we%20have%20tried.%20After%20the%20supreme%20court%20said%20it%2C%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20tried%20to%20talk%20things%20through%20and%20it%20benefitted%20us%20by%20making%20the%20Muslim%20folk%20realise%20that%20fighting%20will%20not%20amount%20to%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Court%20announced%20its%20decision%2C%20we%20reached%20a%20compromise%20with%20the%20Muslims%20(The%20Sunni%20central%20board)%20where%20they%20agreed%20to%20take%20back%20any%20claims%20on%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20And%20after%20this%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20did%20the%20decision%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20we%20not%20reached%20this%20agreement%2C%20the%20verdict%20would%20not%20have%20been%20this.%20Since%20the%20Muslims%20had%20let%20go%20of%20claims%2C%20then%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20this%20verdict.%20This%20happened%20only%20through%20discussion%2C%20as%20all%20problems%20can%20be%20solved%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20continue%20harbouring%20animosity%2C%20then%20some%20men%20can%20satisfy%20their%20egos%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20society%20suffers.%20I%20believe%20that%20wise%20Muslims%20should%20also%20come%20forward%20to%20end%20these%20fights%20through%20dialogue%20for%20the%20long-term%20well-being%20of%20the%20country.%20112%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Shankaracharya%20Ji%2C%20the%20interview%20you%20are%20giving%20me%20will%20be%20seen%20by%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20BJP%20ministers%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%20but%20possibly%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20might%20see%20it.%20The%20BJP%20has%20said%20that%20the%20person%20introducing%20politics%20into%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20yourself%20and%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eperhaps%20the%20other%20Shankaracharya.%20Fake%20claims%20about%20you%20are%20being%20made%20online.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20you%20have%20visited%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%20to%20spread%20a%20chaadar.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20this%20treatment%20of%20yourself%20by%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20a%20shankaracharya%2C%20one%20of%20the%20four%20great%20swamis%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20How%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20the%20government%20saying%20that%20you%20are%20politicising%20matters%20and%20fake%20stories%20are%20being%20spread%20about%20you%20online%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20that%20till%20now%20I%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20visit%20the%20city%20of%20Ajmer%20at%20all.%20When%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20to%20the%20city%2C%20how%20will%20I%20go%20to%20Ajmer%20Sharif%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20planned%20to%20go%20to%20each%20district%20of%20Rajasthan%20so%20I%20will%20go%20to%20Ajmer%20but%20till%20now%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20go%2C%20so%20reaching%20the%20dargah%20is%20not%20possible.%20Even%20if%20I%20do%20go%20to%20a%20dargah%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20I%20will%20not%20become%20a%20Muslim.%20I%20will%20not%20be%20praying%20to%20Allah.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20see%20why%20I%20went.%20So%2C%20our%20PM%20who%20people%20consider%20to%20be%20a%20bigger%20Hindu%20than%20the%20Shankaracharyas.%20In%20Champat%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20words%20he%20is%20Lord%20Vishnu%20himself.%20Does%20he%20not%20go%20to%20dargahs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20seen%20his%20videos.%20He%20sends%20and%20spreads%20chaadars%20to%20various%20dargahs.%20So%20just%20by%20being%20there%2C%20did%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20become%20a%20Muslim%3F%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20if%20the%20shankaracharya%20goes%20to%20some%20place%20then%20accusing%20him%20so%20quickly%20is%20a%20way%20of%20propaganda%20and%20destroying%20his%20image.%20I%20have%20only%20ever%20known%20this%20saint%20called%20Ramdev%20Pir%20whose%20devotee%20Arvind%20came%20to%20show%20support%20for%20our%20movement%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20and%20then%20invited%20us%20to%20his%20ashram%2C%20where%20the%20samadhi%20of%20the%20pir%20is%2C%20I%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20puri%20and%20another%20renowned%20priest%20went%20there%2C%20which%20are%20the%20images%20being%20circulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20says%20that%20you%20are%20a%20Congress%20supporter.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20say%20baseless%20things%2C%20Proof%20is%20needed%20for%20substantiation.%20Show%20me%20proof%20of%20me%20ever%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20the%20party%2C%20fighting%20an%20election%20from%20their%20side%20or%20promoting%20the%20party.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20BJP%20or%20Congress%2C%20but%20mere%20opportunists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20is%20that%20they%20also%20called%20my%20guruji%20a%20Congress%20supporter%2C%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20the%20Congress.%20In%201992%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHD)%20joined%20with%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20make%20Narasimha%20Rao%20the%20PM.%20Boota%20Singh%20was%20the%20Home%20Minister%20and%20Dawood%20Dyal%20quit%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20VHP%20where%20they%20caused%20issues%20near%20the%20contested%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20have%20visited%20and%20covered%20it.%20When%20my%20guruji%20opposed%20it%20by%20saying%20it%20was%20wrong%2C%20he%20was%20called%20pro-Congress%20when%20we%20were%20protesting%20their%20actions%20while%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20had%20joined%20with%20them.%20He%20is%20the%20person%20who%20proposed%20that%20the%20temple%20should%20be%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20not%20150kms%20far%20by%20giving%20examples%20of%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura.%20That%20is%20his%20contribution%20and%20he%20fought%20with%20the%20Court.%20No%20one%20went%20to%20the%20court%2C%20but%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20went%20to%20court%20because%20the%20BJP%20was%20saying%20that%20the%20court%20could%20not%20interfere%20in%20religious%20matters%2C%20but%20he%20promoted%20going%20to%20court%20and%20won.%20We%20are%20letting%20them%20build%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20at%20least%20they%20should%20obey%20the%20scriptures.%20Do%20we%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20say%20that%20much%20in%20our%20religion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShankaracharya%20Ji%2C%20my%20last%20question%2C%20in%20this%20interview%2C%20your%20innermost%20sadness%20will%20be%20clear%20to%20the%20audience.%20This%20is%20the%20time%20when%20every%20Hindu%20should%20have%20been%20celebrating%20with%20happiness%20but%20instead%20the%20shankaracharyas%20are%20unhappy.%20Instead%20of%20happiness%2C%20this%20is%20a%20sad%20moment%20for%20you..%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20for%20us%2C%20but%20for%20many%20Hindus%20like%20us%20who%20care%20about%20religion%20and%20not%20politics.%20The%20President%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%20said%20that%20he%20collected%2010-15%20crore%20people%20by%20missed%20calls%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20becomes%2022%20crores%20if%20you%20combine%20the%20RSS.%20Then%2C%20there%20are%20other%20small%20factions%20who%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20total%20of%2025-30%20crores.%20Out%20of%20100%20crore%20Hindus%2C%20even%20if%2025%20crore%20is%20with%20them%2C%20the%20remaining%2075%20crore%20are%20religious%20Hindus%20and%20not%20political%20Hindus%20who%20stay%20away%20from%20dirty%20politics.%20That%2075%20crore%20is%20unhappy%20because%20they%20respect%20the%20scriptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20politicised%20Hindus%20are%20happy%2C%20the%20religious%20Hindus%20are%20unhappy%20because%20we%20want%20the%20PM%20to%20decide%20and%20shift%20the%20date%20to%20a%20further%20one%20so%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20completed%20and%20can%20be%20established%20according%20to%20the%20scriptures%2C%20so%20everyone%20is%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20is%20your%20message%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20want%20to%20request%20him%20and%20say%20that%20if%20someone%20has%20said%20this%20is%20a%20way%20of%20opposing%20you%2C%20then%20that%20is%20untrue.%20We%20want%20a%20PM%20who%20makes%20good%20decisions.%20You%20are%20a%20good%20orator%2C%20if%20you%20obey%20the%20scriptures%2Cand%20don%E2%80%99t%20become%20tyrannical%2C%20then%20you%20are%20a%20good%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Varanasi%20when%20they%20broke%20important%2C%20ancient%20temples%2C%20we%20did%20have%20a%20saint%20contest%20elections%20against%20him.%20We%20hate%20Aurangzeb%20because%20we%20were%20told%20he%20broke%20temples%2C%20then%20why%20will%20we%20forgive%20one%20of%20our%20own%20to%20do%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20you%20talking%20about%20the%20Kashi%20corridor%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20building%20the%20Kashi%20corridor%2C%20when%20they%20broke%20temples%20and%20idols%20we%20opposed%20them%20and%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20we%20will%20do%20it%20again%20if%20this%20happens%20again.But%2C%20I%20am%20not%20anti-modi%20because%20there%20is%20no%20father%20in%20the%20country%20who%20has%20never%20yelled%20at%20his%20son%20for%20his%20mistakes.%20If%20he%20learns%20from%20those%20mistakes%2C%20everything%20is%20okay.%20We%20are%20only%20opposing%20your%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShankaracharya%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20are%20saying%20to%20Mr.%20Modi%20as%20if%20he%20was%20your%20son%2C%20to%20postpone%20the%20Pram%20Pratishtha%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20time%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20day%2C%20wait%20for%20the%20temple%20to%20be%20completed%2C%20then%20do%20it%20according%20to%20the%20scriptures%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20and%20by%20doing