D%20King%20said%20the%20soul%20of%20America%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20never%20be%20saved%20so%20long%20as%20it%20destroys%20the%20deepest%20hopes%20of%20men%20the%20world%20over.%E2%80%9D%20He%20warned%20that%20America%20had%20lost%20moral%20authority%20abroad%20and%20derided%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20deadly%20Western%20arrogance%20that%20has%20poisoned%20the%20international%20atmosphere%20for%20so%20long.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20pointed%20to%20the%20role%20of%20the%20US%20in%20prohibiting%20the%20realisation%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20revolutionary%20government%20seeking%20self-determination%E2%80%9D%20in%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20poignantly%20in%20that%201967%20speech%20at%20Riverside%20Church%2C%20King%20detailed%20the%20devastating%20costs%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20described%20the%20millions%20of%20children%20and%20women%20who%20were%20killed%20by%20American%20bombs%20and%20bullets%20and%20the%20poor%20masses%20who%20were%20spared%20slaughter%20only%20to%20face%20a%20slow%2C%20painful%20death%20by%20disease%20and%20starvation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20King%20turned%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20North%20Vietnamese.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20we%20do%20not%20condone%20their%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20King%20said%20in%20the%20speech%2C%20%E2%80%9Csurely%20we%20must%20see%20that%20the%20men%20we%20supported%20pressed%20them%20to%20their%20violence.%20Surely%20we%20must%20see%20that%20our%20own%20computerized%20plans%20of%20destruction%20simply%20dwarf%20their%20greatest%20acts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20King%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fight%20for%20justice%20and%20humanity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%E2%80%99s%20words%20resonate%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20King%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataforprogress.org%2Fblog%2F2023%2F12%2F5%2Fvoters-want-the-us-to-call-for-a-permanent-ceasefire-in-gaza-and-to-prioritize-diplomacy%5C%