a.com%2F229014%2Findia-farmer-agriculture-reforms-central-government-nirmala-sitharaman-essential-commodities-act-contract-farming-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20positive%20impact%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20society.%20This%20idea%2C%20once%20planted%2C%20lingered%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20New%20Year%20resolution%20to%20serve%20society.%20%E2%80%9CI%20happened%20to%20visit%20an%20orphanage%20located%20on%20Mysore%20Road.%20Despite%20being%20well-run%2C%20it%20lacked%20several%20amenities%2C%20and%20there%20were%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20children.%20When%20I%20visited%20in%20January%2C%20considering%20the%20climate%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20area%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20children%20were%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanathya%20Foundation%20provides%20free%20medical%20equipment%20to%20people%20in%20need%20for%20free.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-2-1704891555-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcap